\id MRK  
\h SAN MARCOS 
\toc1 A JE'RA' U JACH TSOYIR U T'…ÖN C'UJ TU TS'IBTA MARCOS 
\toc2 SAN MARCOS 
\toc3 Mr. 
\mt1 A JE'RA' U JACH TSOYIR U T'…ÖN C'UJ TU TS'IBTA MARCOS 
\c 1  
\s1 Juan, a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac tu tsec'tic ich t åc åy ru'um 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ3.1‚Äë12; Lc.‚ÄØ3.1‚Äë9, 15‚Äë17; Jn.‚ÄØ1.19‚Äë28) 
\p  
\v 1 U jach tsoyir u t' ån Jesucristo u parar C'uj caj u y ånxchun bic a je' ts'iba'an a ra' cu bin tarej. 
\p  
\v 2 Tu y ånxchun an ten bic Isa√≠as u ts'ibm ån uch quire' raji' ts'a'b u tucur ten C'uj quir u ts'ibtic a ba' u c'at C'uj. U'yex ba' tu ts'ibtaj: 
\q1 Iric, quij C'uj, quin tuchi'tic y åjtseq'uir in t' ån, quij C'uj, p åyber cu tsoyquintic a ber tu ca bin c'uchur.  
\v 3 Ti' y ån mac tan u c'am t' ånic ich t åcay ru'um. Raji' tan ya'aric: ‚ÄúTajquintex a worex soc c'ucha'an a worex a qui' acsiquex Jaj Ts'ur irex tan a jariquex u ber rey quir u tar.‚Äù 
\m Baxuc caj u ts'ibtaj Isa√≠as uch. 
\m  
\v 4 Rajen c'uchij Juan tan u yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac ich t åcay ru'um tan u tsec'tic ca' u c'axej tu yor mac soc u p' åticob u c'asirob soc u jawsa' u si'pirob ten C'uj.  
\v 5 Tiri' caj r åc binob yicn ån Juan tu cotor mac a c åja'anob tu ru'umin Judea quet bayiri' tu cotor mac ti' u cajar Jerusal√©n. Tu toc arajob ba' c'asir caj u betob quir u jawsa' u si'pirob ten C'uj. Jeroj tune', caj acsa'b ja' tu jo'rob ten Juan ich u ya'arir Jord√°n. 
\p  
\v 6 A Juano' u buquinm ån u noc' a s åcta'b ti' u tsotser u y år åc' camello. Tu c' åxaj u n åc' yejer ot'. Raji' cu chi'ic sac'. Cu m åquic cab a m å'  åcr åc'a'an.  
\v 7 Caj u tsec'taj Juan: 
\p ‚ÄïTan u tar tin pach a mac jach no'j. A teno' ‚Äïquij Juan‚Äï, m å' no'jen. M å' pataren, a teno', cax in chen p'uxtar in pitic u c'anin u pech' x ån åb.  
\v 8 A teno' ‚Äïquij Juan‚Äï, caj in wacsaj ja' ta jo'rex chen a mac a ca' bin c'uchuc je' u ts'ic techex u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj. 
\s1 Acsa'b ja' tu jo'r Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ3.13‚Äë17; Lc.‚ÄØ3.21‚Äë22) 
\p  
\v 9 M å' uch caj ruq'uij Jes√∫s ich u cajar Nazaret, ra' u wa'an u ru'umin Galilea. Caj c'uchij Jes√∫s yicn ån Juan caj acsa'b ja' tu jo'r xan ich u ya'arir Jord√°n.  
\v 10 Caj ts'oc u yacsic ja' tu jo'r Jes√∫s ten Juan tan u bin ich chi' ja', Jes√∫s seb caj u yiraj u buj ca'anan. A jeroj caj yiraj xan, u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj tan yeman irej susuy caj oc yicn ån Jes√∫s.  
\v 11 Raji' caj u yubaj u t' ån a cu tar ca'anano', caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïA techo' ‚Äïquij‚Äï, in pararech, in jach yajech. A techo' ta qui'quin tin wore'. 
\s1 Tumta'b u yor Jes√∫s ten Satan√°s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ4.1‚Äë11; Lc.‚ÄØ4.1‚Äë13) 
\p  
\v 12 A jeroj tune', seb caj pay u ber Jes√∫s ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj ca' xic ich t åcay ru'um.  
\v 13 Tiri' y ån Jes√∫s uch ich t åcay ru'um quir u tumta' u yor ten Satan√°s, raji' u ts'urir a quisino'. Caj tumta'b u yor ten Satan√°s cuarenta q'uin. Caj tumta'b yor Jes√∫s ten Satan√°s quir u yiric wa cu yacsic u si'pir. Ti' y ån c'axir b åc' tu y ån Jes√∫s, chen tarob u y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj quir u yamta'rob Jes√∫s. 
\s1 Jes√∫s tu y ånxchun u tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj ich u ru'umin Galilea 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ4.12‚Äë17; Lc.‚ÄØ4.14‚Äë15) 
\p  
\v 14 Chen caj ts'oc u c' åric Juan tu cu naj ma'c år mac, c'uchij Jes√∫s ich u ru'umin quir u tsec'tic u jach tsoyir u t' ån a cu tar ich C'uj.  
\v 15 Raji' Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïBaje'rer, c'uchij tu q'uinin a caj u ya'araj C'uj uch. Baje'rer cu bin reyinbir C'uj, rajen c'axex a worex soc a p' åtiquex a c'asirex, ca wacsiquex ta worex a jach tsoyir u t' ån C'ujo'. 
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u p åyaj xib, a r åc y ån u nub xib a cu chuquicob c åy 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ4.18‚Äë22; Lc.‚ÄØ5.1‚Äë11) 
\p  
\v 16 A ray u q'uinino' tan u man Jes√∫s ich u chi' c'ac'nab, u c'aba' u c'ac'nabir Galilea, jeroj caj u yiraj Sim√≥n yejer u yits'in Andr√©s. Tu chuquicob c åy quire' ra' u beyajob. Cu chuquicob c åy yejer yajow chim.  
\v 17 Caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïSayenex tin pach quir in camsic techex in t' ån soc a manex a tsec'tex in t' ån ich a wet winiquirex jud√≠o. 
\p  
\v 18 Seb caj u p' åtajob u chuc c åyob, caj sayob tu pach Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 19 Wa ber caj bin m å' nachi', a jeroj caj u yiraj Jacobo, u parar Zebedeo, yejer Juan u yits'in Jacobo. Robob caj u chuyob u chimin u chuc c åyob ich u chemob.  
\v 20 An ten bic caj u yiraj ti'ob, seb caj pay Jacobo yejer Juan ten Jes√∫s. A jeroj tune', caj u p' åtajob u tetob Zebedeo ich chem yejer u c'urewo', caj sayob tu pach Jes√∫s. 
\s1 Ti' y ån xib turiri', y ån u c'ac'as quisinin 
\r (Lc.‚ÄØ4.31‚Äë37) 
\p  
\v 21 Caj c'uchob tu cajar Capernaum. Ber caj c'uchij tu q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åjob u winiquirob jud√≠o, caj oquij Jes√∫s tu chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj oquij tu y ånxchun u camsa'ob.  
\v 22 A mac a ti' y ånob a caj u yubob jach jaq'uij yorob an ten bic caj u camsaj ti'ob. M å' ja wirej, Jes√∫s caj u camsaj, jach noj u camsej mac. M å' an ten bic y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s.  
\v 23 A ray u q'uinino' seb caj oquij ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o a mac aca'an quisin ti'e'. Raji' c'am caj u ya'araj: 
\p  
\v 24 ‚ÄïBa' a c'at ti' a tenobo' Jes√∫sech a cu tar ich u cajar Nazaret? Tara'anech a ch'esiquenob, in werechob maquechi', a techo' a mac a cu tar ich C'uj, a techo' caj a ric'saj a w åc' ås b åjiri' soc C'uj y åninech. 
\p  
\v 25 Jes√∫s caj u q'ueyaj, caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïNup a chi', ca' joc'aquech, ca' a p' åtej a je' xiba'. 
\p  
\v 26 A c'ac'as quisino', caj u betaj ca' baban åqui', jeroj tune' caj joq'uij ti', tan u c'am aw åt.  
\v 27 A mac a ti' y ånob ich u chan naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o jach manan r åc jaq'uij yorob, rajen caj u pacran c'aticob ich u yet winiquirob jud√≠o: 
\p ‚ÄïBa'quiri' a jera', quij ya'ara'ob? Ba' u jer t' ån cu camsa'? Quire' cu camsa' an ten bic mac y ån u muc'. M å' ja wirej, a je' xiba', cax cu t' ånic a quisino', cu quibicob a ba' cu ya'ara'ob ti' ten Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 28 Caj joc'ob a mac a ti' y ånob ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob c'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o seb caj u jumbintajob a ba' caj u yirob ich tu cotor u ru'umin Galilea, baxuc xan, caj u jumbintob a ba' caj u yubajob. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic u yixquit Sim√≥n Pedro 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.14‚Äë15; Lc.‚ÄØ4.38‚Äë39) 
\p  
\v 29 Wa ber caj ruq'uij Jes√∫s ti' u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujintiob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, yet binacob u cams åwinicob. Yet binacob Jes√∫s a Jacobo yejer Juan, bayiri' xan Sim√≥n Pedro yejer Andr√©s, a jeroj caj c'uchob tu yatoch Sim√≥n Pedro yejer Andr√©s.  
\v 30 Barej u yixquit Sim√≥n Pedro characbar quire' jach ar u jo'r. Seb caj ara'b ti' Jes√∫s yaj u yixquit Sim√≥n Pedro.  
\v 31 C'uchij tun, raji', caj u m åchaj u c' åb caj u ric'saj, jeroj seb caj jaw, caj u y ånxchun u jansa'rob. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic pim mac 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.16‚Äë17; Lc.‚ÄØ4.40‚Äë41) 
\p  
\v 32-33 Tan u bin u q'uinin caj jach ac'bich åjij tun. Tu cotor a mac a p'eri' u cajarob yejer Sim√≥n Pedro yejer Andr√©s caj c'uchob tu cu naj ocar mac tu yatoch Sim√≥n Pedro yejer Andr√©s. Caj tar purbirob a mac a jach yaj ich Jes√∫s yejer a mac a aca'an ti' quisino'. Tiri' caj u r åc much'quintajob u b åj tu y ån Jes√∫s.  
\v 34 Caj u jawsaj ya'ab mac yejer ya'ab u yajirir. Bayiri' xan, caj u joc'saj ti' mac a y ån ya'ab u quisinino'. M å' ju cha'b år u joc'ar u t' ånob ten Jes√∫s quire' u jach erob jach raji' Cristo. 
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u tsec't u t' ån ich u ru'umin Galilea 
\r (Lc.‚ÄØ4.42‚Äë44) 
\p  
\v 35 C' ås a'ac'bir m å' toy qui' sasich åj åqui' caj ruq'uij Jes√∫s tu junan tu m åna' mac soc u t' ånic C'uj.  
\v 36 Jes√∫s cu man c åxta'bir ten Sim√≥n Pedro yejer u yet cams åwiniquirob.  
\v 37 Wa ber caj irir Jes√∫s ten a mac tarob c åxta'bir. Caj u ya'arob: 
\p ‚ÄïTu cotor mac cu c åxtiquechob. 
\p  
\v 38 Caj ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïCa' xico'onex ich u jer cajarob a bayt åco' ca' in tsec'tej xan, quire' rajen ruq'uen ti' a ray cajaro'. 
\p  
\v 39 Jes√∫s r åc man ich tu cotor u ru'umin Galilea cu yocar jujuntur tu chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o tiri' caj u tsec't u t' ån C'uj. Jujuntur u cuchir tu cu naj tsec'tic u t' ån C'uj tu oquij caj u joc'saj a mac aca'an u quisinin ti'. 
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u jaws a mac u c ånm ån iq'uer u ca' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.1‚Äë4; Lc.‚ÄØ5.12‚Äë16) 
\p  
\v 40 A mac a ju c ånm ån iq'uer u ca', c'uchij yicn ån Jes√∫s, caj xonr åj caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïWa ja c'ate', c'ucha'an a wor a jawsic iq'uer u ca' ten. 
\p  
\v 41 Jes√∫s caj u tucraj ti', caj u nuncaj caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïIn c'at ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, jawen quen. 
\p  
\v 42 A jeroj tune', seb caj jawij a iq'uer u ca' ti'.  
\v 43 Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj ca' xic tan u chich aric ti': 
\p  
\v 44 ‚ÄïM å' a bin a wa'aric tu ca man bic jawech. Chen tar a bin ich sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o quir a sijic ti' a ba' caj ya'araj Mois√©s uch. Soc yerob tu cotor mac jawsa'bech ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 45 Raji' m å' caj u yubaj a ba' ara'b ten Jes√∫s, seb caj u toc r åc araj ich u rac'ob. Caj yubob jaw a iq'uer u ca' ti'e'. Rajen Jes√∫s m å' c'ucha'an yor u joc'ar ich tu cotor mac cax a ba' cajarob. Cu chen joc'ar tu m åna' mac, cax ti' cu bin Jes√∫s ti' r åc c'uchob yicn ån Jes√∫s. 
\c 2  
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a m å' u ch'ictare' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ9.1‚Äë8; Lc.‚ÄØ5.17‚Äë26) 
\p  
\v 1 M å' ya'ab u q'uinin caj w åc' ås urij Jes√∫s ich u cajar Capernaum. A jeroj caj yubob u juminta'b, ti' y ån Jes√∫s ich yatoch.  
\v 2 Seb caj u much'quintajob u b åj ich Jes√∫s jach pim, cax tu cu naj ocar mac ich yatoch m å' u p'atar tu cu yocar mac quire' pech. A Jes√∫so' caj u tsec'taj u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj ti'ob.  
\v 3 Caj tar purbirob yicn ån Jes√∫s a mac a m å' u ch'ictar. M å' ya'ab caj tar purbirob cuatro xib tan u c'ochicob ti'.  
\v 4 Chen m å' c'ucha'an yorob u nats'arob yicn ån Jes√∫s quire' a pimo'. Tar nacob ich pach naj, caj u r åc pa'aj u pach naj soc u yens å'r a mac a m å' u ch'ictar tu yicn ån Jes√∫s. Yej u tas caj emsa'b ich Jes√∫s. M å' ja wirej, m å' c'ucha'an yorob u yocarob ich naj tu yicn ån Jes√∫s uch.  
\v 5 A Jes√∫so' caj u yiraj bic caj u yacsob tu yorob wa Jes√∫s c'ucha'an yor u jawsic caj u ya'araj ti' a mac a m å' u ch'ictare': 
\p ‚ÄïIn yajech ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, toc jaw a si'pir. 
\p  
\v 6 Chen ti' y ån m å' ya'ab y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s ti' cura'anobi'. Tu yorob tu tucrajob ti' Jes√∫s:  
\v 7 ‚ÄúBiquinin baxuc cu tsicbar a ray xibo'? A baywo' poch' u ca'. Je' wa ju ch'uchur u yor u jawsic u si'pir maque', chen u b åjiri'o' C'uj c'ucha'an yor u jawsic mac?‚Äù  
\v 8 Chen seb caj u yubaj Jes√∫s tu pixam a ba' tu mucu tucrajob, rajen caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin a baxuco' ca tucriquex ta pixamex?  
\v 9 Wa quin wac ti' a je' a m å' u ch'ictare': ‚ÄúTin jawsaj a si'pir‚Äù, a techexo', m å' a werex wa y ån in muc' ti' C'uj wa m å' y ån in muc' ti' C'uj. Barej wa quin wac ti': ‚ÄúRiq'uen ca' xiquech‚Äù, je' a werex y ån in muc' ti' C'uj.  
\v 10 Caj ara'b ten Jes√∫s ti' y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s: ‚ÄúArej in wesej techex y ån u muc' ten C'uj quir in jawsic u si'pir mac ich yoc'ocab quire' baxuquenechexo', quij.‚Äù 
\p Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj a mac a m å' u ch'ictare': 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄïRiq'uen ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ch'aj a tas ca' xiquech ich a watoch. 
\p  
\v 12 A mac m å' u ch'itare' caj riq'uij caj u ch'aj u tas caj joq'uij  åc åtan tu cotor mac rajen tu cotor mac jach jaq'uij yorob caj u r åc qui' t' åntajob C'uj: 
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj. M å' biq'uin ij quiram ånex a baxuc a jera'. 
\s1 Lev√≠ t' ån ten Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ9.9‚Äë13; Lc.‚ÄØ5.27‚Äë32) 
\p  
\v 13 Caj joc' Jes√∫s caj bin ich u chi' c'ac'nab u c'aba' Galilea. Tu cotor a pimo' tarob tu yicn ån Jes√∫s, a jeroj tune', caj u y ånxchun u camsic ti'ob.  
\v 14 Carique' tan u man wa ber caj u yiraj Lev√≠, u parar Alfeo curucbar tu cuchir tu cu naj c' åmic u taq'uin gobierno romano. Caj p åyir ten Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïCux ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, quir a c ånic in t' ån. 
\p Caj riq'uij, caj bin tu pach Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 15 Pachir ti' y ån Jes√∫s ich yatoch Lev√≠. Curucbar jan ån Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob, yejer a mac a cu c' åmicob u taq'uin gobierno romano. Ti' y ån xan, a mac a m å' patarob, p'eri'ob u jan ånob yejer Jes√∫s. Quire' y ån ya'ab mac cu sayob tu pach quir u c ånicob u t' ån Jes√∫s.  
\v 16 U cams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s a fariseojo' caj u yirajob curucbar jan ån u ca' Jes√∫s yejer a mac a cu naj c' åmicob u taq'uin gobierno romano yejer a mac a m å' patarob, caj u ya'arob ti' u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin a w åjcams åy åjirex ‚Äïquij ya'araj ti'‚Äï p'eri' u jan ånob yejer a mac a cu naj c' åmicob u taq'uin u gobierno romano, bayiri' xan, yejer a mac a m å' patarobe'? 
\p  
\v 17 A ber caj u yubaj Jes√∫se', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA m å' yajo', m å' u c'atic ts'ac, quire' toc y ån yor. A mac a yajo' ra' cu bin c åxtic yo'och ts'ac. Rajen tareno'. Quire' taren in p åyic a mac a y ån u si'pirob ca' u c'axej tu yorob soc u p' åticob a c'aso'. M å' taren in p åyic a mac a cu ya'aricob m åna' u si'pirob. 
\s1 U c'atbar yubej wa cu p' åtic u jan ån 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ9.14‚Äë17; Lc.‚ÄØ5.33‚Äë39) 
\p  
\v 18 U cams åwinicob Juan yejer cams åwinicob a fariseojo' tan u jamach p' åticob u jan ånob soc u qui' c'ujinticob C'uj. Caj tarob c'ata'bir ti' ten jun yarob mac caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin u cams åwinicob Juan yejer u cams åwinicob a farisejo' cu jamach p' åticob u jan ånob soc u qui' c'ujinticob C'uj, barej a cams åwinicob m å' u jamach p' åticob u jan ånob quir u qui' c'ujinticob C'uj? 
\p  
\v 19 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA mac a cu bin u ch'ic u raque', cu p åyic u rac'ob quir u qui' qui' jan ånob. A tarobe', m å' tsoy wa cu tucricob.  
\v 20 Barej wa cu c'uchur tu q'uinin cu bin, a tu ch'aj u raq'ue', jeroj a ray u q'uinino' cu bin u jamach p' åticob u jan ånob. Wa ber ca' bin xiquen a ray u q'uinino' jach jaj cu bin u jamach p' åticob u jan ånob in cams åwinicob. 
\p  
\v 21 Caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' tsoy xan, ca' a xaxactiquex a ba' caj a c ånex ti' a nunquirex yejer a ba' ca c åniquex ti' ten. M å' ja wirej, m åna' mac cu jomp åc'tic u rabir u noc' yejer ric'ben. Cu mosar a ric'beno' cu jatar, cu cochtar. Jach carim u jorir u noc' u cochtar.  
\v 22 Bayiri' xan, m åna' mac cu t'ajic u c'ab u wich uva ich u rabir yot'er chivo. Quire' ca' bin pajn åc, cu bujur, hasta u r åc wecar u c'ab uva. Cu r åc jatar u yot'er chivo xan. A ric'ben u c'ab u wich uva, ca' u t'ajej ich ric'ben yot'er chivo soc m å' u bujur soc m å' u r åc wecar u c'ab uva. 
\s1 U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj u jich'tob u p åc'ar u wich trigo tu q'uinin tu cu jesic u b åjob winiquirob jud√≠o 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.1‚Äë8; Lc.‚ÄØ6.1‚Äë5) 
\p  
\v 23 Ra' u q'uinin tu cu jesic u b åjob u winiquirob jud√≠o, cu ch' åtob u cor mac Jes√∫s, quet yejer u cams åwinicob. Robob caj u tarob tu pach Jes√∫s. U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj u jich'tajob u p åc'ar u wich trigo, u jantejob quire' wich åjob.  
\v 24 A winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' tun, caj u ya'arob ti' Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïIric a cams åwinicob. Biquinin cu jich'ticob u p åc'ar u wich trigo u q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Quire' cu beyajob tu q'uinin tu cu jesic u b åjob u winiquirob jud√≠o. 
\p  
\v 25 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo': 
\p ‚ÄïM å' wa ta xacajex tu ts'iba'an u t' ån C'uj ti' David uch ber caj wich åjij David yejer u rac'ob uch?  
\v 26 Caj oquij David yejer u rac'ob ich naj tu t'ina'an yot'er chivo quir u c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj ts'a'b yo'och pan ten a sacerdote. A ra u q'uinino' ti' y ån u jach ts'urir sacerdote u c'aba' Abiatar. A jeroj tune', caj u jantajob David yejer u rac'ob quire' wich åjob, cax m å' tsoy u jantic a caj ts'a'b ti' David ten sacerdote. M å' ja wirej, ra' quir u ts'ab år ti' C'uj, cu chen janticob a sacerdotejo'. 
\p  
\v 27 Bayiri' xan, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' ja wirej, u q'uinin tu cu jesic u b åjob ra' beta'b ti' winic quir u jesic u b åjob. M å' beta'b winic ten C'uj ti' u q'uinin tu cu jesic u b åjob.  
\v 28 A teno', baxuquenechex, chen a teno' cu ts'uririntiquen tu cotor ba', inan a ba' cu yiric mac tu q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s. 
\c 3  
\s1 A xibo' a m å' u jitir u c' åbe' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.9‚Äë14; Lc.‚ÄØ6.6‚Äë11) 
\p  
\v 1 Caj w åc' ås oquij Jes√∫s ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujintiob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o ich u cajar Capernaum. Ti y ån uch turiri' xib a m å' u jitir u c' åb.  
\v 2 Y ån jun yarob u c'at u pac' årob u pach Jes√∫s rajen caj u qui'qui' p åctob quir yiricob wa je' u jawsic mac tu q'uinin tu cu jesic u b åjob u winiquirob jud√≠o.  
\v 3 Jes√∫s tun, caj u ya'araj ti' a mac a m å' u jitir u c' åbo': 
\p ‚ÄïRiq'uen ca' taquech chumuc tu y åno'onex, soc ch åca'an yiriquech tu cotor mac. 
\p  
\v 4 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob 
\p ‚ÄïY ån ba' quir in c'atic techex ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. Ba' cu cha'b år a to'onex ca' ic betex u t' ån Mois√©s tu q'uinin tu quic jesic ic b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o? C'ucha'an yor mac u betic a ba' jach tsoy, wa c'ucha'an yor mac u betic a ba' c'as? C'ucha'an yor mac u yamtic mac u jer, wa c'ucha'an yor mac u quinsic mac? 
\p Barej a pimo' m å' ju nucobi'.  
\v 5 Jes√∫s caj u r åc p åctaj yirej jujuntur, jach ts'ic u wich Jes√∫s quire' caj u yiraj m å' ju tucrob a m å' u jitir u c' åb ten u yet winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj u yiraj jach chich u jo'rob. Caj u ya'araj ti' a mac a m å' u jitir u c' åbo': 
\p ‚ÄïTich' a c' åb ca'anan. 
\p A xibo' caj u tich' u c' åb seb caj toc qui' jaw u c' åb.  
\v 6 Caj joc' tun u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' caj u much'quintob u b åj yejer u yet winiquirob jud√≠o a cu ya'aricob herodiano quire' cu say årob tu pach u rey Herodes. Caj u sebquintajob u much'quinticob u b åj quir u p'eri'quintajob u tucurob quir u quinsicob Jes√∫s. 
\s1 A pimo' ich u chi' c'ac'nab 
\p  
\v 7 Barej Jes√∫s caj bin yejer u cams åwinicob tu chi' c'ac'nab. Caj sayob tu pach ten Jes√∫s a jach pim mac a tar u tarob tu ru'umin Galilea.  
\v 8 Bayiri' tarob ti' u ru'umin Judea yejer a mac a c åja'anob tu cajar Jerusal√©n, yejer a mac a c åja'anob pichir u ya'arir Jord√°n tu cu tar q'uin, yejer a mac a c åja'an tu ru'umin Idumea, yejer a mac a c åja'anob bayt åc tu cajar Tiro yejer u cajar Sid√≥n. P'enc åch pim tarob yicn ån Jes√∫s quire' caj u yubob a ba' caj u betaj Jes√∫s a ba' a m åna' mac iram ån biq'uin.  
\v 9 Quire' jach manan pim a mac a tarob rajen Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob ca' u c åxejob chem quir u yocar. Yubic cu max år. Yiric cu r åc nactanticob u b åj ich Jes√∫s.  
\v 10 M å' ja wirej, caj u yirob caj u jawsaj ya'ab mac rajen a mac a yajob cu nactanticob u b åj ich Jes√∫s caj u t årejob u noc' quir u jaw år u yajiriro'.  
\v 11 Wa ber a mac a aca'an quisin ti' caj tarob caj u purajob u b åj  åc åtan ti' Jes√∫s, cu c'am aw åt tu cu ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïA techo' u pararech C'uj. 
\p  
\v 12 Barej raji' Jes√∫s caj u jach q'ueyaj quisin soc m å' u ya'aricob mac Jes√∫s. 
\s1 Teta'b ten Jes√∫s a mac a cu bin u tsec'ta'r u t' ån 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ10.1‚Äë4; Lc.‚ÄØ6.12‚Äë16) 
\p  
\v 13 A jeroj tune', Jes√∫s caj u nacajtaj u p'uc wits caj u p åyaj a mac u c'at u p åyic. Robob caj binob ti' quir u camsa'rob.  
\v 14 Caj u tetaj doce xib soc ti' y ånob tu yicn ån, soc ca' bin tuchi'tacob ten Jes√∫s quir u tsec'ticob u t' ån.  
\v 15 Bayiri' xan, ts'a'b u muc' ti'ob ten Jes√∫s quir u joc'sicob quisin, bayiri' xan, ts'a'b u muc' ti'ob ten Jes√∫s quir u jawsicob a mac a yajo'.  
\v 16 A jera' u c'aba'ob a doce xibo' a teta'b ten Jes√∫s. A jera' Sim√≥n a mac caj u ts'aj u c'aba' Pedro.  
\v 17 A jera' Jacobo u parar Zebedeo yejer Juan u yits'in Jacobo, ti' mac caj u ts'aj u jer u c'aba'ob Boanerges, u c'at ya'arique', U Parar A Cu Peco', quire' ts'icob.  
\v 18 A jera' Andr√©s, a jera' Felipe, a jera' Bartolom√©, a jera' Mateo, a jera' Tom√°s, a jera' Jacobo, u parar Alfeo, a jera' Tadeo, a jera' Sim√≥n, a cu say år tu pach cananista.  
\v 19 A jera' Judas Iscariote, a mac pachir caj u c'ubaj Jes√∫s. 
\s1 Pac' u pach Jes√∫s aca'an quisin ti' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.22‚Äë32; Lc.‚ÄØ11.14‚Äë23; 12.10) 
\p Caj ts'oc u tetic Jes√∫s ti'ob yet binacob tu yatoch.  
\v 20 U jer jach pim tarob rajen m å' u cha'b år u jan ån quire' jach pim cu tarob.  
\v 21 Barej caj u yubajob u jach u b åjob Jes√∫s, r åc tarob quir u chuquicob Jes√∫s quire' cu ya'aricob uch: 
\p ‚ÄïJaj ix t åcoj, m åna' u yor a Jes√∫so'. 
\p  
\v 22 Bayiri' xan, u cams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s a tar u tarob tu cajar Jerusal√©n. Pac' u pach Jes√∫s ten u cams åyirob u t' ån Mois√©s quire' caj u ya'arob wa aca'an quisin ti': 
\p ‚ÄïAca'an Beelzeb√∫ ti' m å' ra' ts'ic u muq'ui' u ts'urir quisin. U muc' u ts'urir quisin Beelzeb√∫ caj u joc'sej quisin. 
\p  
\v 23 Rajen Jes√∫s caj u t' ånajob ca' tacob u much'quinticob u b åj caj u ya'araj ti'ob tu cu camsicob: 
\p ‚ÄïA Satan√°so' bic tabar u w åc' ås b åjiri' u joc'sic? M å' c'ucha'an yor u joc'sic u w åc' ås b åjiri'.  
\v 24 M å' ja wirej, wa ju w åc' ås b åjiri' cu bin ts'ictar ich u ru'umin tu cu reyinticob rey, je' u r åc ch'esicob u b åj.  
\v 25 Cax wa ju w åc' ås b åjob tu yatoch cu ts'ictarob je' u r åc quinsicob u b åj.  
\v 26 Bayiri' xan, a quisino', u jach c'aba' Satan√°s, wa ju yet quisinin bin u joc'sejob, jeroj caj u toc ch'esob u b åj, jeroj m åna' quisin. 
\p  
\v 27 ‚ÄôBic tabar in joc'sic quisin wa m å' tin y ån ch'esaj u muc' u jach ts'urir quisin, Satan√°s? A baywo' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, c'ucha'an in wor in joc'sic quisin. Quire' aro' irej a mac a oquij ich yatoch a mac chich u muc' irej wa tu c' åxaj soc u r åc ch'ic u ba'tac. 
\p  
\v 28 ‚ÄôTaj quin wa'aric techex, tu cotor u si'pirob bin jawsac ti' mac ten C'uj, cax a ba' poch'n åjij uch bin jawsac ti' xan.  
\v 29 Barej, a mac a cu p'astic u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj m å' biq'uin cu bin jawsabir u si'pir, munt q'uin sipn åjij. 
\p  
\v 30 Baxuc caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s quire' y ån jun yarob tus yarm ånob uch: ‚ÄúY ån quisin ti' Jes√∫s.‚Äù 
\s1 U n å' yejer u yits'inob Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ12.46‚Äë50; Lc.‚ÄØ8.19‚Äë21) 
\p  
\v 31 Caj tarob tun u yits'inob yejer u n å' Jes√∫s, chen p'atob ich tancab yatoch tu y ån Jes√∫s, caj u tuchi'tajob t' ånbir.  
\v 32 A ya'ab maco' ti' cura'anob yicn ån Jes√∫s, robob caj u ya'arajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIric, a n å' cu t' åniquech, ti' y ån yejer a wits'inob ich tancab cu c åxtiquech yiriquech a n å' yejer a wits'inob. 
\p  
\v 33 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj ti'ob tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïTaj ca wa'aric ra' in n å' yejer in wits'inob. 
\p  
\v 34 Caj u p åctaj a jach ya'ab mac a cura'anob yicn ån Jes√∫so', caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïA je'ra' irob in n å', a jera' irob in wits'inob.  
\v 35 Quire' cax a mac a cu betic a ba' u c'at C'uj ra' irej in n å' ra' irej in jach its'inob. 
\c 4  
\s1 Y åjq'uich'iny åjir 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.1‚Äë9; Lc.‚ÄØ8.4‚Äë8) 
\p  
\v 1 Jes√∫s caj w åc' ås bin ich u chi'c'acnab u c'aba' Galilea caj u y ånx chun u camsic b åyt åc tu y ån u chi'c'ac'nab. Jach ya'ab mac caj u much'quintob u b åj yicn ån Jes√∫s rajen caj oquij ich chem a ti' y ån ich c'ac'nab caj curajij. Tu cotor a mac ti' y ånob ich ru'um tu chi' c'ac'nab.  
\v 2 Caj u ya'araj ya'ab ba' tu cu camsa'rob. Tu cu camsa'rob caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p  
\v 3 ‚ÄïU'yex a ba' quin camsic techex. Caj bin mac quir u p åq'uic u p åc'ar ich u cor.  
\v 4 A mac caj bin u q'uich'intej ich u cor. Carique' caj u q'uich'intaj caj rub jun yar u p åc'ar ich tam bej. Caj tar u ruq'uic ch'ich'.  
\v 5 U jer jun yar rub ich tunich tu m å' pim u ru'umin. Seb caj ts'ern åj quire' jay u ru'umin, rajen seb caj joc'.  
\v 6 Barej caj naquij q'uin caj quimij m å' tu bin ocac u mots, rajen quimij.  
\v 7 U jer jun yar caj u r åc q'uich'intaj, caj rub ich q'ui'ix. Caj ch'ijij caj r åc bobosta'b ten q'ui'ix m å' ju ts'ajaj u wich.  
\v 8 U jer jun yar caj u r åc ca' q'uich'intaj ich u jer u ru'umin. Jach tsoy u ru'umin. Caj ts'ern åj, caj ch'ijij, caj u nets'aj u wich. Cien caj u toc ts'aj u wich. U jer caj u ts'aj u wich sesenta. U jer caj u ts'aj u wich treinta. 
\p  
\v 9 U'yex ba' quin camsic techex soc a wu'yiquex, soc a najtiquex a ba' u c'at ya'aric. 
\s1 Biquinin cu camsic ti'ob 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.10‚Äë17; Lc.‚ÄØ8.9‚Äë10) 
\p  
\v 10 Caj ts'oc u camsa' ten Jes√∫s caj u juts' u b åj u doce cams åwinicob Jes√∫s tu yicn ån, quet yejer a mac a ti' y ånob b åyt åc ti'. Caj ara'b ti': 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin ca camsic a pimo' bic tabar u q'uich'intic u p åc'ar ich u cor? 
\p  
\v 11 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïJe' u ts'ic techex C'uj quir a najtiquex a ba' caj u mucu araj ten C'uj ti' Cristo. Chen a pimo' m å' ju bin u najtejob quire' m å' ju c' åmajob u t' ån C'uj. Tu chen so'soc u'yajob camsa'rob.  
\v 12 Rajen, a mac a m å' yerob C'uj a cu yubicob in camsicob cu chen u'yicob cax cu yubicob m å' ju najtejob. M å' bin u c' å'oticob soc u yacsicob tu yorob soc u toca'rob ten C'uj. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu tajquintic u cams åwinicob a ba' quiri' m å' ju najtajobi' 
\p  
\v 13 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' ja najtajex a je' ba' caj in camsajechex. Bic tabar ca bin a najtex tu cotor a ba' ca so'soc u'yiquex in camsiquechex?  
\v 14 A mac a caj bin u q'uich'intic u p åc'ar ich u cor raji' cu q'uich'intic u yijir u t' ån C'uj.  
\v 15 Y ån jun yarob mac ich tan bej tu cu q'uich'ita'r u t' ån C'uj, barej caj u yubob seb caj tar Satan√°s u taquic ti' mac u t' ån C'uj a ba' yubm åni' soc m å' ju najticobi', irej u yijir a rub ich tan bej a caj in camsajechex sam.  
\v 16 U jer jun yarob mac, robob irob u yijir a q'uich'inta'b ich u tunich robob caj yubob u t' ån C'uj qui' yorob caj u c' åmajobi'.  
\v 17 Quire' robob irej u yijir a m å' tam oc u mots. Seb caj u toc p' åtajob u t' ån C'uj caj yubajob u tumtaj u yorob. Caj yubajob u chucur u pachob quire' u t' ån C'uj, rajen caj u p' åtajob u t' ån C'uj.  
\v 18 U jer jun yarob irob u yijir a q'uich'inta'b a rub ich q'ui'ix, robob a tu yubob u t' ån C'uj.  
\v 19 Chen a je' maca' cu tucric u t'ajar u ba'tac yejer u t'ajar u taq'uin yejer u beyaj. A ba' y ån yoc'ocab cu pachtic, rajen bob åsta' u t' ån C'uj soc m å' c'ucha'an yor u qui'quintic u yor C'uj irej q'ui'ix caj u bob åstaj tu q'uich'inta'b.  
\v 20 A rub yijir tu tsoy u ru'umin ra' quir u camsiquechex a mac a caj u jach c' åmaj u t' ån C'uj, caj u ts'aj u wich cien, ra' cu qui' man tu tsoyir. U jer caj u ca' ts'ajaj u wich sesenta, ra' cu man tu tsoyir chen m å' c'ucha'an yor ti' a caj u ts'aj u wich cien. U jer caj u ts'ajaj u wich treinta, ra' cu man tu tsoyir chen m å' c'ucha'an yor ti' a caj u ts'ajaj u wich sesenta. 
\s1 U t' ån quir u camsic ti' quib 
\r (Lc.‚ÄØ8.16‚Äë18) 
\p  
\v 21 Bayiri' xan Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïM åna' mac cu yacsic u quib yaram u ch'ac, m å' ich yaram rec xan. M å' ja wirej, cu t' åquintic ca'anan quir u yerc'ac'tic yatoch. Rajen a ba' cu camsic ti'ob irej wa t' åba'an u quib.  
\v 22 Bayiri' xan, tu cotor ba' a mucutaca'an tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj baje'rer, ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' u joc'ar u tajire'. Baxuc tu cotor mac je' u c' å'otic ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin je' u yubique'.  
\v 23 U'yex ba' quin camsic techex soc a wu'yiquex soc a najtiquex a ba' u c'at ya'aric. 
\p  
\v 24 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob xan: 
\p ‚ÄïQui' u'yex soc m å' ju tubur techex a ba' ca wu'yiquex. Wa chichin ca wu'yiquex u t' ån C'uj chichin cu bin u camsic techex. Wa ya'ab ca wu'yiquex u t' ån C'uj jeroj ya'ab cu bin u camsic techex.  
\v 25 A mac a y ån u t' ån C'uj ti'e' u c'at u qui' najtic, C'uj cu bin u camsic ya'ab. Chen a mac ti', chichin u t' ån C'uj, m å' u c'at u qui' najtic, je' u p' åtique'. 
\s1 Quir u camsic ti' u yijir a cu ch'ijire' 
\p  
\v 26 Jes√∫s tu cu camsic caj u ya'araj xan: 
\p ‚ÄïTu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj ra' irej tu cu man mac cu p åq'uic u yijir ich ru'um.  
\v 27 Rajra' cu wen ån, rajra' cu yajar, jeroj u man u q'uinin cu yiric a ba' u c'at. U yijir a caj u p åc'aje' ts'ern åj, jeroj cu ch'ijir. Chen m å' yer bic tabar u ch'ijiri'.  
\v 28 M å' ja wirej, u b åjiri' u ru'um tu junan cu ch'isic u yijir a p åc'a'an ti', cu c' ås ch'ijire', cu joc'ar u re'. Cu ts'ocar u ch'ijire' cu jobar yi'ij. Cu jobar yi'ij cu tar u wich.  
\v 29 Cu tijire' seb cu jaq'uic quire' c'uchuc tu q'uinin u jaq'uic. 
\s1 Quir u camsic ti' u yijir mostaza 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.31‚Äë32; Lc.‚ÄØ13.18‚Äë19) 
\p  
\v 30 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj xan: 
\p ‚ÄïAn bic je' in quetquintic tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj? An bic tabar je' in camsic techex? A ba' t' ånin quin wa'aric techex?  
\v 31 An ten bic u ch'ijir u p åc'ar mostaza xib ich ru'um. M åna' u jer p åc'ar jach ne mijin yijir mostaza.  
\v 32 Cu ch'ijire' jach manan u xit'ir u c' åb. U jer p åc'ar m å' u ne xit'ir u c' åb. Hasta ch'ijir u che'er a jeroj, cu tar ch'ich' u c' åxicob u c'u' ich u bo'oy. 
\s1 Biquinin Jes√∫s cu camsic a jera' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.34‚Äë35) 
\p  
\v 33 Yejer jach ya'ab a je' camsa'bir u t' ån an ten bic a jera' caj u ya'araj ti'ob u t' ån hasta tu c'ucha'an yorob u najtejob.  
\v 34 Wa m å' yejer a camsa'bir t' ån m å' ju tsicb åtej ti'ob ba', barej caj u toc araj tu cotor ba' ti' u cams åwinicob caj bin tu junanob. 
\s1 Jes√∫s tu t' ånaj yic'ar quir u ch'enan bayiri' u yamin 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.23‚Äë27; Lc.‚ÄØ8.22‚Äë25) 
\p  
\v 35 Ra'iri' u q'uinin caj bin q'uin caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' u cams åwinicob: 
\p ‚ÄïCuxex tanxer ich c'ac'nab. 
\p  
\v 36 Caj ts'oc u tuchi'tic a ya'ab maco', toc ti' y ån chem caj toc oquij Jes√∫s quet yejer u cams åwinicob. Yet binacob u jer jun yarob chem.  
\v 37 A jeroj caj tar ch'ic yum yic'ar, caj tar u yamin xan, tan u burur u chemin, tabar u jurur u chem.  
\v 38 Raji'e', tan u wen ån. Y ån u c'anjo'r tu cu wen ån ich yach chem. A'as Jes√∫s ten u cams åwinicob, caj u ya'arob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirechob, m å' wa ca tucriquenob? Tabar in jururob. 
\p  
\v 39 Caj ajij Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj yic'ar ca' ch'enac: 
\p ‚ÄïXurej, ic' ‚Äïquij‚Äï. M å' a tar. 
\p A jeroj, ch'en u tar yic'ar, caj ch'en u yamin c'ac'nab xan.  
\v 40 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin tu jac'saj a worex, m å' wa ja wacsm ånex ta worexi'? 
\p  
\v 41 Caj u jach ch'aj ch'ic yum sajaquirob, caj u pacran arajob ich u yet cams åwinicob: 
\p ‚ÄïA mac a je' xiba' cu yuba'r u t' ån cax a ic'o' cax u yamin c'acnab cu quibicob u t' ån Jes√∫s? 
\c 5  
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a mac aca'an quisin ti'e' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ8.28‚Äë34; Lc.‚ÄØ8.26‚Äë39) 
\p  
\v 1 Caj c'uchob pichir c'ac'nab Galilea, ti' u ru'umin a cu ya'aricob Gadarajo'.  
\v 2 Jes√∫s tan tu joc'ar ich chem, a jeroj seb caj joc' tu t'aja'an u baquer u quimiriro' turiri' xib a mac aca'an quisin ti'e'.  
\v 3 Ti' c åja'an ich tu t'aja'an u baquer u quimiriro'. M åna' mac c'ucha'an yor u c' åxic cax yejer mascab a irej sumo'.  
\v 4 A ucho' chuquij ten u rac'ob caj c' årij yoc yejer mascabir a irej sumo', bayiri' xan yejer u mascabir c' åb chen caj u p'icaj u mascabir c' åb caj u xexet'aj u mascabir yoc. M åna' mac c'ucha'an yor u suquintic quire' jach manan chich u muc'.  
\v 5 U burur ac'bir yejer u burur q'uin cu man uch aw åt u ca' ich tu t'aja'an u baquer u quimiriro', bayiri' xan, ich wits, bayiri' xan, cu man u c'ubic u b åj yejer tunich.  
\v 6 Barej caj u yiraj Jes√∫s u tar nachir, ra' caj u c' ånaj yacab caj xonraj ich Jes√∫s.  
\v 7 C'am aw åtn åjij caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïBa' a c'at ten Jes√∫s? A techo' u pararech C'uj a mac u C'ujir ca'anan. Quin chich c'atic tech tu quin chuquic C'uj, m å' a ts'ic ten in muc'yaj. 
\p  
\v 8 M å' ja wirej, baxuc caj ya'araj a mac a aca'an quisin ti'e' quire' sam ara'b ti' ten Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïJoq'uen ti' a maca' a techo' quisinech. 
\p  
\v 9 Sam caj u c'ataj ti' quisin: 
\p ‚ÄïBa' a c'aba'? 
\p Caj u nuncaj, tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïLegi√≥n in c'aba'. M å' ja wirej, pimenob aca'anenob ti'. 
\p  
\v 10 Rajra' tan u c'ata' ti' Jes√∫s ten a mac a aca'an quisino' m å' u tuchi'ta'rob tanxer ru'um.  
\v 11 M å' nenach tu y ån Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob, ti' y ån y år åc' cajij q'uec' ån, jach pimob. Cu manob u jan ånob xiw ich p'uc wits.  
\v 12 Caj u chich c'atajob ti' tu cotor a quisinobo' a aca'anob ich a ray xibo' tan ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïArej in binob ich a ray cajij q'uec' ånob quir in ca' wocarob ich a ray q'uec' ånob. 
\p  
\v 13 Seb cha'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s, a jeroj caj joc'ob a quisinob caj ocob ich cajij q'uec' ånob. Tu cotor a cajij q'uec' åno' caj u c' ånajob yacab tu ch'inca'an wits caj u r åc purob u b åj ich c'ac'nab caj r åc quimij. Dos mil q'uec' ån caj quimij. 
\p  
\v 14 R åc puts'ob tun, a mac a cu c ånanticob y år åc' cajij q'uec' ån quire' jaquij yorob. Jeroj caj binob u jumintejob ich u cajarob, bayiri' xan ich mac a ti' y ånob tu corob. Caj joc'ob u yirob a ba' u ber ti'.  
\v 15 Caj r åc c'uchob yicn ån Jes√∫s. Caj u yirajob a mac a aca'an ti' a quisino' Legi√≥n uch, a jeroj caj u yirajob curucbar u buquinm ån u noc', baje'rer y ån yor xan, robob caj u ch'ajob sajquir.  
\v 16 A y åj'irirob caj u tsicb åtajob ba' u ber ti' a mac a aca'an quisin ti'e' Legi√≥n u c'aba' uch, bayiri' xan, a ba' u ber ti' a cajij q'uec' åno'.  
\v 17 Rajen caj y ånxchun u ya'aricob ti' Jes√∫s ca' xic Jes√∫s nachir soc m å' ti' y åni'. 
\p  
\v 18 Jes√∫s caj u yocar ich chem caj c'uchij a mac a aca'an quisin ti'e' a Legi√≥n u c'aba' uche', caj u chich c'ataj ti' ca' xic tu pach Jes√∫s.  
\v 19 Barej a Jes√∫so' m å' ju chaj u tar tu pachi' barej caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïXen ich a watoch ich a b åjob. Xen jumintej an ten bic caj in yajquin tech. Arej yubej u jach carem beyaj caj u betaj C'uj ti' tech. Arej yubej bic joc'sa'b tech quisin ten Jaj Ts'ur. 
\p  
\v 20 A ray xibo' a joc'sa'b u quisinino' caj joc' caj y ånxchun u tsicb åtic u ru'umin Dec√°polis tu cotor ba' a beta'b ti' ten Jes√∫s. Tu cotor mac a caj u yubajob caj jaq'uij yorob. 
\s1 U parar a Jairojo' xquic yejer a xquic a tu t åraj u noc' Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ9.18‚Äë26; Lc.‚ÄØ8.40‚Äë56) 
\p  
\v 21 Barej Jes√∫s caj u w åc' ås ch' åctaj a c'ac'nabo' ich chem tanxer pichir. Tiri' ich chi' c'ac'nab caj u much'quintajob u b åj a pimo' ich yicn ån Jes√∫s.  
\v 22 Caj c'uchij turiri' xib u jach ts'urir u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, Jairo u c'aba'. Barej caj u yiraj Jes√∫s caj tar p'uxtar  åc åtan Jes√∫s ich yoc.  
\v 23 Caj u chich c'ataj ti', tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïCojen ‚Äïquij‚Äï, jawsej in chan parar xquic quire' tabar u quimin. Cojen ca' a ts'anc' åbtej ca' jawac, soc u cuxtar. 
\p  
\v 24 Caj bin Jes√∫s yejer raji', barej jach pim caj sayob tu pach Jes√∫s, cu r åc nactanticob u b åj yicn ån Jes√∫s.  
\v 25 Tiri' ich a pimo' a sayob tu pach Jes√∫s ti' y ån turiri' xquic. M å' u tsoytar uch. Y ån manij doce yaxq'uin caj u c ånaj u yajir.  
\v 26 Cax ts'ac åc ten a mac a yerob ts'ac m å' u tsoytar quire' aro' caj u r åc xupaj u taq'uin yejer u ba'tac, barej m å' yamta'bi' chen cu jach qui' c'astar.  
\v 27 A ray xquico' caj u yubaj tsicb åta'r Jes√∫s. Caj c'uchij ich u pim ån a yaje' caj tar tu pach Jes√∫s caj u t åraj u noc' Jes√∫s.  
\v 28 Quire' cu ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïWa quin t åric u noq'ue', chen u noc' quin t årique', je' in tsoytare'. 
\p  
\v 29 Seb caj ts'oc u t åric u noc' Jes√∫s tsits u q'uiq'uer a xquico', caj u yubaj tu winquirir caj jawij.  
\v 30 Jeroj seb caj u yubaj Jes√∫s caj u jawsaj u yajir mac quire' caj u yubaj u bin u muc' caj ts'oc u tar år u noc'. Jeroj caj u sut u b åj caj u p åctaj a pimo', caj c'ata'b ti': 
\p ‚ÄïMac, t år in noc'? ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 31 U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj u ya'arajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIric a jach pim mac a cu nactanticob u b åj ta wicn ån, biquinin ca wa'aric: ‚ÄúMac t år in noc'?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Jes√∫s raji' caj u p åctaj a mac a u b åc'rism ånobi' Jes√∫s quir yiric a mac t år u noc'.  
\v 33 A xquic tuno', sajacch åjij cu quiquir ånc år quire' yer ba' u ber tu winquirir caj u n åts'aj u b åj yicn ån Jes√∫s caj xonr åj caj u ya'araj ti' tu cotor jach jaj.  
\v 34 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïXquic, quire' caj a wacsaj ta wor ti' ten rajen jawech. Xen in jach yajech ca' qui'ac a wor. Ca' qui' tsoyaquech. 
\p  
\v 35 M å' toy ts'ocaqui' u tsicbar Jes√∫s, jeroj caj c'uchob jun yarob mac yicn ån Jairo, ti' u tarob ich yatoch Jairo u jach ts'urir u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, caj tarob caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïQuimij ‚Äïquij ya'ara' ti' Jairo‚Äï a chan parar xquic. Tsire'ej, cax m å' u tar a w åjcamsay åjir. 
\p  
\v 36 Barej seb caj u yubaj Jes√∫s rajen caj u ya'araj ti' Jairo: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' a ch'ic sajaquir, chen acsej ta wor ten. Y ån tsire'ej ya'aricobe' quim a chan parar xquique'. 
\p  
\v 37 M å' ju chaj u bin mac tu pach Jes√∫s, chen Pedro bin tu pach Jes√∫s yejer Jacobo yejer Juan, u yits'in Jacobo.  
\v 38 Caj c'uchob taro' tu yatoch u jach ts'urir u chan naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o caj u yiraj jumrac yoc'arob quire' cu yac'ticob.  
\v 39 Caj ts'oc u yocare' caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin a jumrac a woc'arex? A teno' quin wiric wen ån u ca', cax a techexo' ca wiriquex quimen a chan xquico'. 
\p  
\v 40 Caj p'asta'b Jes√∫s ten a mac a ti' y ånob tu yatoch Jairo quire' yerob jach quimij a chan xquico'. Barej raji'e' caj ts'oc u r åc joc'sic tu cotor mac tancab, caj acsa'b u tet yejer u n å' a chan xquico' yejer a mac a yet taracobe' caj ocob tu quimen a chan xquico'.  
\v 41 Jes√∫s caj u m åchaj u c' åb a chan xquico' caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïTalita cumi ‚Äïu c'at ya'aric: Chan xquic quin wa'aric tech, riq'uen. 
\p  
\v 42 Seb caj riq'uij a chan xquico', caj y ånxchun u ximbar quire' y ån doce yaxq'uin ti' uch. Seb caj jaq'uij yorob, jach manan caj jaq'uij u yorob.  
\v 43 Barej raji' caj u jach chich araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån aquex ti' mac. 
\p Caj u ya'araj ca' ts'abac u jan ån a chan xquico'. 
\c 6  
\s1 P'uspachta'b Jes√∫s ten mac tu cajar Nazaret 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ13.53‚Äë58; Lc.‚ÄØ4.16‚Äë30) 
\p  
\v 1 Caj joq'uij ich Jairo caj bin tu jach cajar. Yet binacob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s.  
\v 2 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o caj oc tu chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o caj oc quir u camsic ti'ob. Ya'ab mac a caj u yubobe', j åpr åj u chi'ob quire' a ba' camsa'bob. Caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïA tub u tar ti' a ray xibo' a je' ba'ra'? Bic tabar ts'a'b u tucur a ti'e' a m å' c'ucha'an yor u betaj a ba' a m åna' mac yiram ån, m å' biq'uin uch a cu jac'ar u yor mac.  
\v 3 A ray xibo' m å' wa ra' cu susche' uchi', u parar Mar√≠a, u sucu'un Jacobo Jos√©, Judas yejer Sim√≥n? M å' wa ti' y ån ånob xan tu y åno'onex u yits'inob a xquicob? 
\p Rajen m å' ju s åjtajobi' cu p'uspachticob ti'.  
\v 4 Barej Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïU y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj, a ts'a'b u tucure' ten C'uj quir u tsicbar a ba' u c'at C'uj m å' u c'at yirir ten yet cajarob tu jach cajar. Cax u w åc' ås u b åjob m å' u c'at yiricob. Chen a mac c åja'an nach u c'at yubicob. 
\p  
\v 5 A taro' m å' c'ucha'an yor u betic a ba' m åna' mac yiram ånob uch m å' biq'uin chen caj u jawsaj jun yarob a mac a yajo'. Caj u ts'anc' åbtaj quir u jawarob.  
\v 6 A Jesuso' jac'a'an yor ti'ob quire' m å' ju yacsajob tu yorob. Pachir Jes√∫s caj c'uchij tu chan cajarob a r åc b åca'an ti' u jach cajar Jes√∫s, caj u camsaj ti'ob. 
\s1 U beyajob a docejo' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ10.5‚Äë15; Lc.‚ÄØ9.1‚Äë6) 
\p  
\v 7 Jeroj, caj t' ånaj yicn ån u doce cams åwinicob, caj y ånxchun u tuchi'ticob ca'ca'turi', caj u ts'ajaj u muc' ti'ob quir u joc'sicob u quisininob.  
\v 8 Caj u jach araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' a ch'iquex bar ich a ber. Chen xomte' ca ch'iquex, baxuc chim m å' a ch'iquex. Baxuc a woj wajex m å' a ch'iquex, baxuc a taq'uinex m å' a ch'iquex ich u poxajir a taq'uinex. 
\p  
\v 9 Chen a pech' x ån åb ca ch'iquex, baxuc turiri' a noq'uex a ch'iquex.  
\v 10 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïWa ber ca' bin acsaquechex ich naj ca' p'ataquechex hasta ca joc'arex ca ca' binex.  
\v 11 Wa ca c'uchurex ich mac a m å' u c'at u yacsiquechex a m å' u c'at u yubicob a t' ånex, ca' joc'aquechex ti' taro'. Puxtex u noy ru'um ta woquex soc yerob y ån u si'pirob quire' m å' u c'atob yubejob a t' ånex. Jach taj quin wa'aric ti' techex, a ray maco' ich a ray cajaro' jach manan ca' bin muc'yajn åcob tu q'uinin u xur t' ån, chen a mac a c åja'anob uch tu cajarjob Sodoma yejer u cajar Gomorra m å' nejach bin muc'yajn åcobi'. 
\p  
\v 12 Jeroj, u doce cams åwinicob caj joc'obe' caj u tsec'tajob ti' mac ca' u c'axej u yorob ca' u p' åtejob u c'asir tu cu manob.  
\v 13 Bayiri' xan, caj u joc'sajob ya'ab quisin tu aca'anob ich mac, caj u jic'tajob tsats quir u jaw år mac a yajo', jach ya'ab jawij. 
\s1 Quinsa'b Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ14.1‚Äë12; Lc.‚ÄØ9.7‚Äë9) 
\p  
\v 14 Baje'rer caj u yubaj rey Herodes u tsicb åticob u c'aba' Jes√∫s a Herodeso' rajen ya'ab mac tus pac' Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r: 
\p ‚ÄïTin t' ån ‚Äïquij‚Äï, w åc' ås riq'uij tu quimirir Juan rajen c'ucha'an yor u betic a m åna' mac yirm ånob uch, m å' biq'uin yirm ånob. 
\p  
\v 15 Chen u jerob juninta'b yubej, caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïRaji' El√≠as u y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj a ts'a'b u tucuric ten C'uj uch. 
\p U jerob caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïRaji' y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj a ts'a'b u tucuric ten C'uj quir u tsicb åtic a ba' u c'at C'uj rajen raji' irej y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj uch. 
\p  
\v 16 Barej caj yubaj Herodese', caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïRaji' Juan, a mac a tin ch' åcaj u car uche', raji' riq'uij tu quimirir. 
\p  
\v 17 M å' ja wirej, raji' Herodes caj u tuchi'taj m åcbir Juan caj u c' åraj tu cu naj m åquic mac. Tiri' tu m åcaj, quire' Herod√≠as u rac' u sucu'un Felipe. M å' ja wirej, Herodes caj u ch'aj u rac' u sucu'un.  
\v 18 M å' ja wirej, caj u ya'araj uch ti' Herodes: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' tsoy a taquic u rac' a sucu'un quire' ra' u toc ch'am ån a sucu'un. 
\p  
\v 19 A Juano' p'acta'b ten Herod√≠as rajen cu ch'uctic quire' u c'at u quinsej barej m å' c'ucha'an u yor ti'.  
\v 20 M å' ja wirej, Herodese' saj åc ti' Juan quire' yer raji' turiri' xib a mac taj yor, a mac a m å' u naj man tu c'asir, rajen cu c ånanta' Juan soc m å' u quinsa'. Tenten caj yubaj cax tucurn åjij quire' tsoy yubic tu xiquin a ba' tsec'ta'b ten Juan.  
\v 21 Jeroj, c'uchij tu q'uinin Herod√≠as cu pajic quir u quinsic Juan. Raji' u q'uinin u c'aba' u rey Herodes, ber cu c' å'oticob u q'uinin caj rocha'b Herodes ten u n å' uch. Rajen caj u p åyaj tu qui'qui' jan ånob u jach ts'urirob a cu yamticob u rey Herodes tu cu reyinticob. Yet payacob a mac u ts'urirob u soldadojob yejer a mac a ney ån u taq'uino' tu ru'umin Galilea.  
\v 22 Barej caj oc tun u parar xquic Herod√≠as, oc'atn åjij tu cuchir tu cu naj qui'qui' jan ånob u rey Herodes yejer u rac'ob. Jach tsoy tu wich u rey Herodes yejer a mac a curucbarob tu cu qui'qui' jan ånob. Rajen caj u ya'araj a reyo' ti' u parar xquic Herod√≠as: 
\p ‚ÄïC'atej ten, cax a ba' a c'at, a teno' je' in ts'ic teche'. 
\p  
\v 23 Caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïC'uj cu yiric ‚Äïquij Herodes‚Äï. Tu cotor ba' ca' a c'atej tene' je' in ts'ic teche' tac tan chumuc u ru'umin tu quin reyinticob. 
\p  
\v 24 Caj joc' raji' u xquic u parar Herod√≠as, caj u ya'araj ti' u n å': 
\p ‚ÄïBa' quin bin in c'atej? 
\p U n å' tune', caj ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïRa' a catej u jo'r Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac. 
\p  
\v 25 Seb caj w åc' ås sutn åjij tu yicn ån rey Herodes caj u c'ataj, cu ya'aric ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIn c'at ca' a ts'ic ten baje'rer u jo'r Juan a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac, ca' a ts'a ten turiri' u r åquir quir in pe'ic. 
\p  
\v 26 M å' jach qui' yor a rey Herodese', tu chen tucric, barej quire' caj u ya'araj: ‚ÄúC'uj cu yiric‚Äù, bayiri' xan, quire' yubob ya'aric tu cotor mac a cu qui'qui' jan ånob rajen y ån u ts'ic ti'.  
\v 27 Seb a reyo' caj u tuchi'taj turiri' u soldado a cu c ånantic a reyo' soc ca' tac purbir u jo'r Juan.  
\v 28 Raji' caj bine' caj u ch' åcaj u car Juan tu cu naj macar mac, caj bin u purej u jo'r ich turiri' u r åquir quir u pe'ic. Jeroj, caj u c'ubaj ti' a ray xquico' u parar Herod√≠as aro' tune' caj u ts'ajaj ti' u n å'. 
\p  
\v 29 Barej u cams åwinicob Juan caj u yubob a ba' u ber, tarob u ch'a'ob u baquer Juan caj u t'ajaj ich turiri' tu cu naj t'ojar u baquer mac. 
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u jansaj cinco mil xib 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ14.13‚Äë21; Lc.‚ÄØ9.10‚Äë17; Jn.‚ÄØ6.1‚Äë14) 
\p  
\v 30 A mac a tuchi'ta'b ten Jes√∫s uch quir u tsec'ta'r u t' ån, caj urob caj u much'quintajob u b åj yicn ån Jes√∫s, caj u tsicb åtajob ti' tu cotor ba' a caj u betob uch, bayiri' xan, yejer a ba' caj u camsob uch.  
\v 31 Raji' tune', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïCuxex ich t åcay ru'um quir a je'siquex a b åj. 
\p M å' ja wirej, ya'ab mac cu tarob bayiri' xan, cu binob, rajen m å' je'erarob m å' quir u man u jan ånob.  
\v 32 P'eri'ob caj r åc ocob ich chem quir u binob ich t åcay ru'um. U tiriri' ti' caj binob soc tu jun ånob.  
\v 33 Irob u binob ten ya'ab mac, caj c' å'ota'bob ten a ya'ab maco'. Rajen caj joc'ob ti' tu cotor u cajarob soc u binob ti' taro' xan, caj u c' ånajob yacab. Ra' bat'an c'uchob a ya'ab maco'.  
\v 34 Barej caj joc' Jes√∫s ich chem, caj u yiraj ya'ab mac toc c'uchob, rajen caj yajquinta'bob quire' irob a t åm ån yucobo' a m åna' y åjc ånany åjir t åm ån yuc. Jeroj tune', caj y ånxchun u camsic ya'ab ba' ti'ob.  
\v 35 Tabar u bin q'uin, caj tarob u cams åwinicob tu yicn ån caj ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïChen t åcay ru'um a tera' m åna' mac c åja'an cu bin q'uin cabar.  
\v 36 Tuchi'tabo' ca' xicob ti' corob, cax ti' u chan cajarob a r åc b åca'anob a tera', ca' u m ånejob yo'och waj quir u jan ånticob quire' m åna' ba' caj u jantob. 
\p  
\v 37 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïTs'ajex yo'och quir u jan ånob ‚Äïquij. 
\p Caj u ya'arajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïJe' wa jin m ånicob yo'och a ya'ab maco' ca' in j åsejob ti'ob. M å' ja wirej, m å' nupa'an u bo'orir yo'ochob, quire' baxuc u bo'orir u beyaj mac turiri' yaxq'uin. 
\p  
\v 38 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïJoq'uenex irex mun pan y ån techex. 
\p Caj ts'oc u yiricobe', caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïY ån cinco pan yejer ca'tur c åy. 
\p  
\v 39 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob u binob u cutarob jujumuch'ob ich su'uc.  
\v 40 P'eri' r åc curajob u tirir ti' junmuch' cura'anob. U tirir ti' caj u cuquintajob junmuch' curicob cincuenta. U jer junmuch' curicob cien.  
\v 41 Jeroj tune', Jes√∫s caj u ch'aj a cinco pano' yejer a ca'tur c åye', caj u p åctaj ca'anan caj u ya'araj: ‚ÄúBayo' C'uj ti' ij co'ochex.‚Äù Jeroj caj u xat'aj a pano' caj u ts'aj ti' u cams åwinicob quir u ca' ts'a'icob  åc åtan a pimo'. Bayiri' xan, caj u j åsaj ti' tu cotor mac a ca'tur c åye'.  
\v 42 R åc janob caj najch åjob xan.  
\v 43 Pachir caj u w åc' ås marajob doce xacob chup yejer u xet'er pan yejer a c åyo'.  
\v 44 A mac a caj u jantob a pano' cuch cinco mil xibob. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ximbar yoc'or ja' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ14.22‚Äë27; Jn.‚ÄØ6.16‚Äë21) 
\p  
\v 45 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob: 
\p ‚ÄïCa' xiquechex ich chem soc a bat'an c'uchurex ich u cajar Betsaida a ti' y ån pichir c'ac'nab. 
\p Quire' raji' cu tuchi'tic a ya'ab macobo'.  
\v 46 Caj ts'oc u tuchi'ticobe' caj bin ich turiri' p'uc wits quir u t' ånic C'uj.  
\v 47 Barej caj ac'birch åjij, a chemo' ti' y ån uch te' ich tan chumuc c'ac'nab. Raji' tune', p'at Jes√∫s tu junan ich ru'um.  
\v 48 Jes√∫s caj u yiraj jach chich tu cu babticob a chemo' quire' caj u nup'ob ic', rajen caj tar Jes√∫s tu yicn ånob tan u ximbar yoc'or a c'ac'nabo'. Jach tabar u sastar caj u yirajob u tar. Jes√∫s u c'at u man p åybej.  
\v 49 U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s tune', caj u yirajob tan u ximbar yoc'or a c'ac'nabo' caj u tucrajob quisin cu tar, caj aw åt åjob.  
\v 50 Quire' tu cotor caj u yirajob, caj u ch'aj saquirob, jeroj, seb t' ånob, caj ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïChichquintej a worex ten ‚Äïquij‚Äï, m å' a ch'iquex sajaquir ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 51 Caj naquij yicn ånob ich a chemo', caj ch'en u tar yic'ar. U cams åwincob Jes√∫s bin yorob quire' jach manan jac'a'an yorob.  
\v 52 Quire' m å' ju c' å'otajob tu yorob u muc', cax caj u yirajob u t'aj år a pano' quire' jach chich u jo'rob. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic u yajirob tu cajar Genesaret 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ14.34‚Äë36) 
\p  
\v 53 Barej caj c'uchob tanxer ru'um tarob tu ru'umin Genesaret, caj u macob a chemo'.  
\v 54 Barej caj joc'ob ti' a chemo' seb c' å'ota'b Jes√∫s ten a maco'.  
\v 55 Caj acabn åjob ti' tu cotor a ti' c åja'anob ich a ru'umo' quir u tarob purbir yicn ån Jes√∫s a mac a yajo'. Caj y ånxchun u tarob u puricob a mac yajo' ti' ch'ac, jaj ix t åco caj u yubob ti' y ån uche'.  
\v 56 Jaj ix t åco te' cu yocarobe' cax wa ju chan cajarob wa ju yajaw cajarob, cax wa ju corob, robob cu tarob purbir mac a yajo' ti' tu cu naj m ånicob yo'och, tiri' cu chich c'aticob ca' u t årejob cax u yoquir u noc'. Tu cotor mac a caj u t årobe', jeroj jaw. 
\c 7  
\s1 A ba' cu yacsic u si'pir maque' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ15.1‚Äë20) 
\p  
\v 1 Caj much'r åjob yicn ån Jes√∫s a ju winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer jun yarob y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Ti' cu tarob tu cajarob Jerusal√©n.  
\v 2 A rayo' caj u yirajob jun yarob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s rajra' caj u jantob waj, u c'at ya'aric, m å' u p'o'ob u c' åbob, rajen caj u p åc'aj u pachob.  
\v 3 M å' ja wirej, a winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer tu cotor u winiquirob jud√≠o cu naj p'o'icob u c' åbob wa m å' u p'o'icob u c' åbob m å' u jan ånob quire' a ba' ara'b ti'ob ten u nunquirob uch.  
\v 4 Barej cu yurob tu cu naj m ånicob yo'och wa m å' u p'o'icob u b åj m å' ju jan ånob. Y ån u jer ya'ab ba' caj u naj c ånajob ti' u nunquirob an ten bic ca' u p'o'ej u ruchir tu cu yuc'ur. Ca' u p'o'ej u p'urir u yo'och ja'. Ca' u p'o'ej u ruchir a mascabo'. Ca' u p'o'ej u ch'ac tu cu wen ån.  
\v 5 Rajen u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer a y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s caj u c'atajobi': 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin a cams åwinicob m å' u cuxtarob an ten bic cu naj camsicob ic nunquirex barej rajra' cu jan ånob? 
\p  
\v 6 Caj u nuncajob raji'e', caj ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïCa'tur a tucurechex a techexo'. Jach taj caj u tsec'taj Isa√≠as ti' tu cotorechex quire' raji' ts'a'b u tucuric ten C'uj quir u ts'ibtic a ba' u c'at C'uj rajen caj u ts'ibtaj: 
\q1 A je' maca', quij C'uj, cu tusaricob: ‚ÄúQuin s åjticob C'uj‚Äù, chen a tu pixamob cu ya'aricob: ‚ÄúJe' wa jin s åjticob C'uj.‚Äù  
\v 7 A C'ujo' cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúBa' wir cu chen c'ujintiquenob wa m å' u quibicob in t' ån? M å' ja wirej, chen u t' ån winic cu quibicob quire' robob cu camsicob u t' ån winic irej wa ju t' ån C'uj cu camsicob.‚Äù 
\m Baxuc caj u ts'ibtaj Isa√≠as uch.  
\v 8 Biquinin ca p' åtiquex u t' ån C'uj quir a qui' c ånantiquex u t' ån a nunquirirex an ten bic u p'obar ruch. Ca' u p'o'ej u ruchir tu cu yuc'ur ca betiquex xan ya'ab u jer ba' an ten bic a jera'. 
\p  
\v 9 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob xan: 
\p ‚ÄïCa wa'ariquex xan, m å' patarex u t' ån C'uj ti' techex, chen a nunquirexo' ca qui' c ånantiquex u t' ån. Ca toc ts'ocsiquex a ba' yarm ånex a nunquirex uch.  
\v 10 Biquinin Mois√©s caj u ya'araj uch: ‚ÄúCa' a s åjtex a tet yejer a n å'. Wa c'as cu tsicbar ti' u tet, ti' u n å' xan, cu joc'sa' quinsbir‚Äù, quij Mois√©s uch.  
\v 11 Barej a techexo', ca wa'ariquex: Wa turiri' parar cu ya'aric ti' u tet wa ti' u n å': ‚ÄúTu cotor ba' a ten y ånin a ca pajiquex u yamtiquechex uche' raji' Corb√°n‚Äù, u c'at ya'aric in toc sijm ån ti' C'uj;  
\v 12 rajen m å' tan a cha'iquex u parar u betic u jer ba' quir u yamtic u tet wa ju n å'.  
\v 13 A baywo' ca c'asquintiquex a ba' ara'b ten C'uj quire' ca qui' c ånantiquex a ba' naj camsa'bechex ten a nunquirex quir a w åc' ås masiquex ti' a pararex. Baxuc ca betiquex ya'ab u jer a ba' an ten bic aro'. 
\p  
\v 14 Caj u w åc' ås t' ånaj tu cotor a ya'ab macobe', caj ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïU'yex ba' quin wac ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ch'aj a najtex.  
\v 15 M åna' ba' a cu jantic mac a cu yasic u si'pir, jari' a ba' cu betic, wa ba' cu ya'aric, ra' cu yacsic u si'pir mac.  
\v 16 U'yex a ba' quin camsic techex soc a wu'yiquex soc a najtiquex a ba' u c'at ya'aric. 
\p  
\v 17 Barej caj oquij Jes√∫s tu japnin naj caj u p' åtaj a ya'ab macobo', jeroj tune', caj c'ata'b ti' ten u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s ba' quiri' caj ts'oc a camsiquenob.  
\v 18 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' wa qui' ca tucriquex ba'? A ba' cu jantic mac m å' ra' cu yacsic u si'piri'.  
\v 19 Quire' a yo'ocho' m å' u yocar tu tucur mac chen ich u n åc', pachir cu joc'ar tu chocher. 
\p A baywo' Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj tsoy u janta' ten a mac a yacsm ånob tu yorob tu cotor yo'och.  
\v 20 Barej caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïM åna' ba' a cu jantic mac cu yacsic u si'pir, jari' a ba cu betic, wa ja ba' cu ya'aric, ra' cu yasic mac u si'pir.  
\v 21 Quire' ich u tucur mac cu joc'ar a ba' cu yacsic u si'pir mac. M å' ja wirej, tu tucur cu joc'ar a c'as u tucuro', tu tucur cu tucric u p åyic xquic wa y ån u mam cax wa m åna' u mam. Tu tucur cu tucric u p åyic xib a y ån u raq'ue', cax a m åna' u raq'ue'. Tu tucur cu tucric u quinsic mac, rajen cu quisic. Tu tucur cu tucric u ya'cric u ba'tac mac, rajen cu ya'cric.  
\v 22 Tu tucur cu tucric u pachtic a ba' y ån ti' u jer mac. Tu tucur cu tucric ba', rajen cu pachtic a xquico' wa ja xibo'. Tu tucur cu tucric ba' rajen cu tus aric mac. Tu tucur cu tucric ba', rajen cu q'uextar yor. Tu tucur cu tucric ba', rajen cu p åq'uic u pach mac. Tu tucur cu tucric ba', rajen m å' u c' åmic u t' ån C'uj. Tu tucur cu tucric ba', rajen m å' u c'ujintic C'uj.  
\v 23 Tu cotor a ray c'aso' cu joc'ar tu tucur mac, rajen cu yacsic u si'pir mac. 
\s1 A xquico' a cu tar ich tanxer ru'um 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ15.21‚Äë28) 
\p  
\v 24 Barej caj ruq'uij taro' caj bin tu ru'umin Tiro yejer u ru'umin Sid√≥n. Caj c'uchij caj oquij ich naj. M å' u c'at yerta' wa ti' y ån ten a ya'ab macobo', barej m å' c'ucha'an yor u taquic u b åj Jes√∫s soc m å' yirir.  
\v 25 Tu juminta' yubej ti' y ån Jes√∫s ich naj, caj c'uchij xquic yicn ån Jes√∫s, caj u puraj u b åj ich u yoc Jes√∫s quir u s åjta'. Raji' y ån turiri' u chan parar xquic a mac aca'an quisin ti'e'.  
\v 26 A xquico' griego u t' ån, chen raji' ti' naj c åja'an tu ru'umin sirofeniciajo'. Caj u chich c'ataj ti' ca' joc'sac a quisino' ti' u chan parar xquic.  
\v 27 Barej Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïCa' y ån bat'an janac u pararob quir u nachaj årob. M å' tsoy u puric u yo'och u pararob ti' a chan pec'obo'. 
\p  
\v 28 A xquico' caj u nuncaj, tan ya'aric ti': 
\p ‚ÄïTaj a ba' ca wac Jaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, cax cu jantic yaran pojche' tu cu jutur u p'up'ir yo'och a chan pararob. A chan pec'o' cu jan ån yaram pojche' tu cu jutur u p'up'ir. 
\p  
\v 29 Jeroj tune', caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïQuire' a je' t' åna' ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ca' xiquech, toc jaw a chan parar xquic ti' u quisinin. 
\p  
\v 30 Caj w åc' ås ur tu yatocho' caj u yiraj u chan parar xquic characbar ich u ch'ac, toc joc'sa'b u quisinin. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a mac a m å' u t' åne' a m å' u yubej t' åne' 
\p  
\v 31 Jes√∫s caj joq'uij tu ca'ten ti' u ru'umin Tiro caj u ch' åctaj u ru'umin Sid√≥n caj c'uchij tu c'ac'nabir Galilea. Caj u ch' åctaj tan chumuc u ru'umin Dec√°polis.  
\v 32 Jeroj caj tar purbir ti' turiri' xib, a m å' u joc'ar u t' åne', a m å' u yubej t' ån xan. Caj u chich c'atajob ti' ca' u ts'anc' åbtej ti' quir u jaw år.  
\v 33 U tiri' ti' caj u p åyaj Jes√∫s a mac a macar u xiquine' soc m å' p'eri' tu y ån a ya'ab macobob. Jeroj caj u ts'aj yar u c' åb tu xiquin a mac a m å' u yubic t' åne', caj tubn åjij Jes√∫s, caj u t åraj u yac' xan.  
\v 34 Caj u nacsaj u wich ca'anan caj u putaj yic', caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïEfata, u c'at ya'aric: Ca' jep åj åc a xiquin ‚Äïquij ya'ara' ten Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 35 Jach seb jaw a m å' u yubej t' ån. Tsoyjij u yac' caj qui' t' ån åj ich u t' ån.  
\v 36 Caj u maquintaj ti'obe': 
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån ariquex ti' mac. 
\p Cax caj u chen maquintaj ti'ob ya'ab tu jen tsicb åtajob.  
\v 37 Jach jaq'uij yorob tun, cu ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïJach tsoy tu beta'r tu cotor, cax inan a m å' u joc'ar u t' ån cu jawsique', cu joc'ar u t' ån a macar u xiquine'. 
\c 8  
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jansic cuatro mil xib 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ15.32‚Äë39) 
\p  
\v 1 A ray u q'uinino', caj ts'oc u much'quinticob ya'ab macob. M åna' yo'och pan bin u jantobi'. Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj u cams åwinicob tu yicn ån, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p  
\v 2 ‚ÄïQuin yajquintic a ya'ab macoba' chen ts'oc u man m åna' u nup u q'uinin ti' y ånob yejerenob baje'rer, u yo'ochob tu r åc xupajob.  
\v 3 Wa quin tuchi'ticob ca' xicob tu yatochobe' je' u rubur u muc'ob ich beje' quire' wi'ij. M å' ja wirej, y ån jun yarob ich a ya'ab macoba' nach tub u tarob. 
\p  
\v 4 U cams åwinicob caj u nuncajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïJe' wa ju c'uchur yor mac ich a je' t åcay ru'uma' ca' u na'ajquintej yejer yo'och pan a je' ya'ab macoba'? M å' ja wirej, m åna' mac te' c åja'anoba'. 
\p  
\v 5 Caj u c'ataj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïMun pan y ån techexi'? 
\p Robobe' caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïSiete pan y ån a tenobi'. 
\p  
\v 6 Caj u ya'araj ti' a ya'ab macobo' ca' curacob ich ru'um. Jeroj caj u ch'aj a siete pano' caj u ya'araj: ‚ÄúBayo' C'uj quire' caj a ts'aj to'onex ij co'ochex‚Äù, jeroj tune', caj u xat'aj caj u ts'aj ti' u cams åwinicob quir u ts'icob  åc åtan a ya'ab macobo'. Robob tune' caj u ts'ajob  åc åtan a ya'ab macobo'.  
\v 7 Y ån xan ti'ob jun yarob maj ån c åyob, jeroj caj u t' ånaj C'uj: ‚ÄúBayo' C'uj quire' caj a ts'aj to'onex ij co'och c åyex‚Äù, caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob ca' ts'abac xan  åc åtan a ya'ab macobo'.  
\v 8 Caj janobe' caj na'ajch åjob, jeroj tune', caj u marajob u xet'er, caj u marajob siete xac chup yejer u xet'er.  
\v 9 A mac janobo' tac cuatro mil. Jeroj tune', caj u ya'araj ti'ob ca' xicob tu yatochob.  
\v 10 Seb caj oquij yejer u cams åwinicob ich chem, caj c'uchob tu ru'umin u c'aba' Dalmanuta. 
\s1 C'ata'b ti' ca' iric carem u beyaj Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ16.1‚Äë4; Lc.‚ÄØ12.54‚Äë56) 
\p  
\v 11 Caj c'uchob a winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' caj y ånxchun u nunquicob a ba' cu tsicbar Jes√∫s, caj u c'atob ti' u esacob ti' ca'anan a ba' m åna' mac yiram ån uch m å' biq'uin yiram ån. M å' ja wirej, cu tumticob u yor Jes√∫s.  
\v 12 Caj ts'oc yubic ya'ara' ti' ten u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' caj u putaj yic', caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïA techexo', a mac cuxa'anob tu q'uinin baje'rer ca c'atic tenex ca' in wesej techex a ba' a m åna' mac yiram ån uch m å' biq'uin yiram ån. Jach taj quin wa'aric techex m å' biq'uin quin bin in wesej ti' techex a ba' a m åna' mac yiram ån uch a m å' biq'uin yiram åno'. 
\p  
\v 13 Jeroj tune', caj u p' åtajobe', caj w åc' ås oc ich chem caj bin tanxer ru'um pichir c'ac'nab. 
\s1 U p åj s åc ånob a winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ16.5‚Äë12) 
\p  
\v 14 U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s tu'ub ti'ob uch u ch'icob yo'och waj, Chen turiri' yo'och waj caj u ch'aj ich chem.  
\v 15 Caj u camsaj ti'ob tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïQui' c ånantechex a b åjex ti' a ba' cu camsic techex u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer a ba' cu camsic techex a mac u yajob u b åj Herodes. A ba' cu camsicob irej a p åj s åc åno'. 
\p  
\v 16 U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj u pacran t' ånajob ich u yet cams åwinicob caj ya'arob: 
\p ‚ÄïRa' ix ti' cu ya'aric quire' m åna' to'onex waj quir ic jan ånex. 
\p  
\v 17 Jes√∫s caj u c' å'otaj u tucurob caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin ca pacran t' åniquex a b åjex quire' tub techex a ch'iquex a wo'och panex? Biquinin m å' a toy c' å'otiquex biquinin m å' a toy najtiquex? Taquij u q'uinin baje'rer chich a jo'rex.  
\v 18 Y ån a wichex biqinin m å' a wiriquex ba'? Y ån a xiquinex biquinin m å' a wu'yiquex t' ån? M å' wa c'aj techex?  
\v 19 Barej caj in xat'aj a cinco yo'och pan ich a cinco mile' mun xac chup yejer u xet'er caj a marajex? 
\p Robob caj u nuncajob: 
\p ‚ÄïDoce xac caj in marob. 
\p Jes√∫s caj u w åc' ås c'ataj ti'ob: 
\p  
\v 20 ‚ÄïBarej caj in xat'aj yo'och pan yejer c åy ich a cuatro mile', mun xac chup yejer u xet'er caj a marex? 
\p Robob caj u nuncajob: 
\p ‚ÄïSiete xac caj in marobi'. 
\p  
\v 21 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin m å' toy a najtajexi'? 
\s1 Ich u cajar Betsaida jawsa'b a ch'op u wich ten Jes√∫s 
\p  
\v 22 Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwincob caj c'uchob tu cajar Betsaida. Caj tar purbir ti' turiri' ch'op u wich, caj u chich c'atajob ti' ca' u t årej quir u jaw år u wich.  
\v 23 Caj u m åchaj tun u c' åb a chop u wicho' caj u joc'saj tancab tu cajar tu y ånob. Caj tuba'b u wich, caj u ts'an c' åb tu boxer u wich caj u c'ataj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïCa wiric wa ba'? ‚Äïcaj c'ata'b ti' ten Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 24 A ch'op u wicho' caj pacatn åjij caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïQuin wiric a maco' an ten bic che', barej quin wiric u manobe' irej che' cu manob. 
\p  
\v 25 Seb w åc' ås ts'anc' åbtaj yoc'or u boxer wich caj u pacat, jeroj qui' tsoyquinta'b u wich, cax nach cu qui' yiric tu cotor.  
\v 26 Caj u tuchi'taj u yatoch, caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån bin a wa'arej ich a je' cajara'. 
\s1 Ara'b ten Pedro ti' Jes√∫s: Cristojech 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ16.13‚Äë20; Lc.‚ÄØ9.18‚Äë21) 
\p  
\v 27 Caj joc' Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob, caj binob ich u cajarob n åts'a'an, u cajar u c'aba' Cesarea Filipo. A ich bejo' caj u c'ataj ti' u cams åwinicob, caj ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïCaj u jumintajob a wu'yajex, ba' cu ya'aricob ten, a macobo'? 
\p  
\v 28 Robob caj u nuncajob: 
\p ‚ÄïJuanech ‚Äïquij‚Äï, a cu yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac bin. U jerob cu ya'aric, El√≠asech. U jerob, cu ya'aric jaj ix ti' y åjtseq'uirech u t' ån C'uj a ts'a'b u tucuric ten C'uj quir u tsicbar a ba' u c'at C'uj. 
\p  
\v 29 Raji' tune' caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïTen wa ca waquenex? 
\p Pedro tune', caj u nuncaj caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïA techo', raji' Cristojech caj u tuchi'tajech C'uj. 
\p  
\v 30 Raji' caj ara'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån bin a wa'ariquex ti' mac wa Cristojen. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ya'aric bin in caj quimin 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ16.21‚Äë28; Lc.‚ÄØ9.22‚Äë27) 
\p  
\v 31 Jeroj tune', caj y ånxchun u camsic ti'ob bin in caj bat'an muc'yaj a teno' baxuquenechexo'. Bin u ca'ob u xurp' åtiquenob u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o, a nuxibo' yejer u jach ts'urirob sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Bin in caj quinsbir barej ca' bin manac m åna' u nup u q'uinin bin in caj w åc' ås riq'uir quir in cuxtar.  
\v 32 Tu qui' toc r åc araj ti'ob quir u najticob. Caj pay Jes√∫s ten Pedro soc u tiri' cu tsicbar caj u majquintaj Pedro caj ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' a y ån aric a quinsa'. 
\p  
\v 33 Raji' tune', caj u sutaj u b åj caj u p åctaj u cams åwinicob caj q'ueya'b Pedro ten Jes√∫s caj ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïJoq'uen Pedro irech a quisino' a Satan√°so' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. M å' a p'usic in wor ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. M å' quet a wor yejer C'uj, quet a wor yejer a xibo' Pedro. 
\p  
\v 34 Caj u t' ånaj ya'ab macob yejer u cams åwinicob, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïAn ten bic ten ca' bin muc'yajn åquen ich in cruz. Baxuc techex ca' bin muc'yajn åquechex quire' caj a c' åmajex in t' ån cax ca quiminex ich a cruzex. Baxuc xan, ca' a p' åtex a ba' ca pachtiquex ta worex wa ja c'atex a c åniquex in t' ån ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï.  
\v 35 Quire' a mac a m å' u c'at u taquic u cuxtar ti' u rac'ob tu cu chucurob u pach ten u rac'ob, quire' caj u yacsaj tu yor ti' in t' ån, bayiri' xan, quire' u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj, ra' cu bin taquic u pixam.  
\v 36 Cax chen toc y ån a ba'taquex ich yoc'ocab chen wa cu sa'tar a pixamex jeroj tune', ba' wir a ba'taquex ich yoc'ocab?  
\v 37 Je' wa ju c'uchur u yor u bo'otic u pixam yejer u ba'tac wa yejer u taq'uin? M å' biq'uini', c'ucha'an yor u bo'otic.  
\v 38 Wa mac cu ch'ic suraquir ten yejer a ba' quin tsec'tic, quire' a je' cuxa'anob mac baje'rer, a cu naj acsicob u si'pirob, bayiri' xan, ti' a je' cuxa'anob mac, a cu naj manob, baxuc ten ca' bin in ch'a'ej suraquir ti', quire' a teno' baxuquenechexo'. Quin bin in ch'ic suraquir ti' ca' bin taquen ich u sasirir C'uj in Tet yejer u muc' u y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj ca'anan. 
\c 9  
\p  
\v 1 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob xan: 
\p ‚ÄïChen taj quin wa'aric ti' techex, y ån jun yarob ich mac a tera' m å' u bin quimin hasta cu yiric bic C'uj cu bin u reyintic yejer u chichir u muc'. 
\s1 Waysa'b Jes√∫s ten C'uj 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ17.1‚Äë13; Lc.‚ÄØ9.28‚Äë36) 
\p  
\v 2 Ti' y ån Jes√∫s uch ich u cajar Cesarea de Filipo tuj u camsaj ti'ob u cams åwinicob. Caj manij seis u q'uinin Jes√∫s caj u p åyaj Pedro yejer Juan yejer Jacobo. Caj binob ich u jo'r wits tu ca'anan u jo'r witsir. Chen robob pay ten Jes√∫s. …Öc åtan u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj waysa'b Jes√∫s.  
\v 3 Caj waysa' u noc' bajen u ba' ja', s åc t'ina'an u noc', baxuc jach cha'aj u noc'. M åna' mac c'ucha'an yor u p'o'ic u noc' an ten bic a ray s åco'.  
\v 4 Seb irir ixbaj Mois√©s yejer ixbaj El√≠as ten u cams åwinicob a m åna' u nupo'. Cu tsicbarob yejer Jes√∫s caj irir ten u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s.  
\v 5 Pedro caj u t' ånaj caj u ya'araj ti' Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir ‚Äïquij‚Äï, jach tsoy te' y åno'onexa' tera'. Arej in chan t åsej paser, u tirir ti' tech, u tirir ti' ixbaj Mois√©s, u tirir ti' ixbaj El√≠as. 
\p  
\v 6 M å' ja wirej, jach jac'a'an yorob u cams åwinicob rajen Pedro caj ya'araj aro' quire' m å' ju qui' tucraj a ba' caj u ya'araj.  
\v 7 Quire' cu tsicbar Pedro caj tarij turiri' u muy årir caj bob åsta'b ten u muy årir caj joc' u t' ån C'uj ti' a ray u muy åriro', tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïA je' in jach parar in jach yaj. Ca' u'yex u t' ån. 
\p  
\v 8 Seb caj u sut u b åj pacatn åjobe' m å' ju w åc' ås irob mac yicn ånob, chen Jes√∫s y ån. 
\p  
\v 9 Quire' cu yemanob ich u jo'r p'uc wits caj u chen qui' araj ti'ob soc m å' ju ya'arob a ba' ts'oc u yiricob hasta ca' bin riq'uiquen tin quimirir a teno' a baxuquenechex.  
\v 10 Tu chen quibajob a ba' ara'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s, chen cu chan ber s åj åj t' ånob tan u ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïA ba' u c'at ya'aric a ca' bin w åc' ås riq'uic tu quimirir? 
\p  
\v 11 Caj u c'atajob ti', tan ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïQuire' tech caj a wa'araj tenob, m å' in y ån bin in wa'aricob wa caj in wirob ixbaj El√≠as yejer ixbaj Mois√©s. Biquinin cu ya'aricob y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s: ‚ÄúRaji' cu bat'an bin tar El√≠as uch quir u p åyic u ber Cristo soc pachir cu tar a Cristojo'‚Äù? 
\p  
\v 12 Caj u nuncaj raji'e', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïTaj ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. El√≠as cu y ån bat'an tar uch quir u p åyic u bej Cristo soc u c'axicob yorob soc u r åc p' åticob u c'asir u winiquirob jud√≠o. Chen arex ten biquinin u ts'iba'an t' ån C'uj cu tsicbar ca' bin muc'yajn åquen a teno' a baxuquenechexo', bayiri' xan ca' bin u xunp' åtenob ten u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o.  
\v 13 A teno' ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, quin wa'aric techex toc tarij El√≠as, bayiri' xan, robob caj u betob ti' tu cotor a ba' caj u pachtajob tu yorob an ten bic ti' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj ti' raji' a ba' u ber. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu jawsic a mac a m å' u joc'ar u t' ån 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ17.14‚Äë21; Lc.‚ÄØ9.37‚Äë43) 
\p  
\v 14 Caj urob Jes√∫s ich u jo'r wits yejer u m åna' u nup cams åwinicob caj tar tu yicn ån a ju cams åwinicob a p'atobo'. Caj urob Jes√∫s yejer m åna' u nup u cams åwinicob jeroj caj u yiraj r åc b åcrista'b ten ya'ab macob. A y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s cu nunquicob u t' ån yejer u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s.  
\v 15 A ray u q'uinino' tune', caj irir Jes√∫s ten a ya'ab macob caj jaq'uij u yorob caj u c' ånajob yacab tu yicn ån quir u r åc t' ånicob.  
\v 16 Raji' caj u c'ataj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin ca nunquiquex u t' ånob a y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s? 
\p  
\v 17 Caj u nuncaj turiri' ich a ya'ab macobo', caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech, taren in puric in parar tech quire' aca'an quisin ti', rajen m å' u joc'ar u t' ån.  
\v 18 Ca' bin chucuc purbir in parar ten quisin tu cu bin man, cu rubsic ru'um, cu yomanc år u chi', cu j åch'ic u coj, cu tochtar u winquirir rajen jach m åna' u muc' xan. Caj in wa'araj ti' a cams åwinicob ca' u joc'sejob ti'e', barej m å' c'ucha'an yorob u joc'sej. 
\p  
\v 19 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA techexo' a mac a cuxa'anechex u q'uinin baje'rer, am biquinin m å' a wacsic ta worex? A mun u q'uinin y ån in p'at år ta wicn ånex quir a wacsic ta worex? Joq'uen ch'a'ej ten. 
\p  
\v 20 Tabar u nats' år ich Jes√∫s, barej caj irir Jes√∫s ten a quisino', jeroj seb tit'ab a pararo', caj rub ru'um caj b åcr ån åjij caj omn åj u chi'.  
\v 21 Caj c'ata'b ti' u tet ten Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïBer ocac quisin ti' a parar? 
\p Caj u nuncaj u tet: 
\p ‚ÄïTu chichanin caj oc quisin ti'.  
\v 22 Ya'ab u tenin cu purur ich c'ac' bayiri' ich ja' quir u quinsic. Barej wa c'ucha'an a wor a betique', joc'sej a quisino'. Yajquintenob ‚Äïquij u tet u parar‚Äï, y åm tenob. 
\p  
\v 23 Jes√∫s tun, caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïWa je' u c'uchur a wor a wacsic ta wore', tu cotor c'ucha'an yor ti' mac a cu yacsic tu yoro'. 
\p  
\v 24 Jeroj tune', seb caj c'am t' ånaj u tet a pararo', caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïQuin wacsic tin wor, wa m å' ti'ti' yam ten. 
\p  
\v 25 Barej caj u yiraj Jes√∫s, cu tar yacabob tu yicn ån a ya'ab macob, jeroj Jes√∫s caj u q'ueyaj a quisino', tan ya'aric ti': 
\p ‚ÄïA techo' a m å' a cha'ej u t' ån, bayiri' a m å' a cha'ej u yubic t' ån. A teno' quin wa'aric tech, joq'uen ti', bayiri' xan, m å' a w åc' ås ocar ti' a chan pararo'. 
\p  
\v 26 Caj awatn åjij a quisino' seb caj tita'b, caj joc' ti', caj p'at an ten bic mac a quimene', rajen ya'ab macob caj u ya'araj: ‚ÄúJeroj quimij, quij.‚Äù  
\v 27 Barej Jes√∫se' caj u m åchaj u c' åb, caj u ric'saj caj ch'iraj. 
\p  
\v 28 Barej caj oc ich naj, u cams åwinicob caj u c'atajob ti' tu junan: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin a tenobe' m å' c'ucha'an in worob in joc'sicob a quisinobi'? 
\p  
\v 29 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïWa ja c'atex ca' a joc'sex baxuc a baywo' ca' a t' åniquex C'uj tu ca jamach p' åtiquex a jan ånex. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu w åc' ås aric bin u caj quimin 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ17.22‚Äë23; Lc.‚ÄØ9.43‚Äë45) 
\p  
\v 30 Caj ts'oc u ruc'urob ti' taro', caj manob tu ru'umin Galilea. M å' ju c'at wa mac u yerob wa ti' y åni'.  
\v 31 Quire' cu camsic u cams åwinicob caj u ya'araj ti'ob uch: 
\p ‚ÄïQuire' bin u caj c'ubiren a teno' ti' mac a cu p'actiquenob a teno' a baxuquenechexo'. Bin quinsaquen ten a ray xibobo', barej ca' bin ts'ocac in quimene' bin in caj cuxtar ca' bin man åc m åna' u nup u q'uinin. 
\p  
\v 32 U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s m å' ju najtob a ba' ara'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s, tu cu camsic ti'ob, sajacch åjob u c'aticob ti'. 
\s1 A mac a jach no'je' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ18.1‚Äë5; Lc.‚ÄØ9.46‚Äë48) 
\p  
\v 33 Caj c'uchob tu cajar Capernaum. Quire' ti' y ånob ich naj caj u c'ataj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBa' ca s åj åj ariquex ich a bej? 
\p  
\v 34 Barej, robobe' m å' tu nuncajob, quire' ich bej cu nunquicob u t' ånob soc yerob mac jach no'j ich u yet cams åwinicob.  
\v 35 Barej caj curaj Jes√∫s tune', caj u t' ånaj a docejo' caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïWa mac u c'at bin p åyber arej u bin pachir soc raji' u c'urewinta'r ten tu cotor mac. 
\p  
\v 36 Jeroj caj u ch'a'aj turiri' chan parar quir u ch'iquintic tan chumuc tu yicn ånob, caj u mec'aj, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p  
\v 37 ‚ÄïWa tsoy ca betiquex ti' a je' chichana', cax ti' u jer xan, quire' ca yajquintiquenex. Tsoy ca betiquenex ten xan. Baxuc tsoy ca betiquex ti' C'uj a mac a caj u tuchi'tajen. 
\s1 Wa mac m å' p'ec yirico'onex p'eri'o'onex xan 
\p  
\v 38 Caj u t' ånaj Juan, tan ya'aric ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åj cams åy åjirech, caj in wirob turiri' mac cu joc'sic quisin. Cu t' ånic a c'aba'. Caj in wa'arob: ‚ÄúTsire'ej‚Äù, quire' m å' u say år ta pach quir u c ånic a t' ån, an ten bic a tenob quin say årob ta pach. 
\p  
\v 39 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïTsire'ej, cax m å' a wa'ariquex ti' quire' m åna' mac c'ucha'an yor u betic tsoy tin c'aba' wa ca' bin ts'ocaque' cu bin u p'astic in c'aba'.  
\v 40 Quire' a mac a m å' u p'actico'onex cu yamtico'onex.  
\v 41 Taj quin wa'aric techex, wa mac je' u ts'ic techex turiri' ruch ja' quir a wu'q'uiquex quire' caj a wacsaj ta worex ti' Cristo, quin wa'aric techex m å' u bin sat år u bo'orir tu cu ts'ic a woj ja'ex. 
\s1 M å' a cha'iquex u tar a si'pirex 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ18.6‚Äë9; Lc.‚ÄØ17.1‚Äë2) 
\p  
\v 42 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA mac a cu yacsic u si'pir u rac'ob a tu c ånaj chichan a caj u yacsaj tu yor. Arej jach manan tsoy ca' u jich'ej ich u car yejer yajaw ca'. Ca' u purej u b åj ich c'ac'nab quire' caj u toc p åyaj u si'pir u rac'ob.  
\v 43-46 Rajen quin wa'aric techex: Xonch' åtej a c' åb wa raji' cu p åyic a si'pirex. Cax a woc wa raji' cu p åyic a si'pirex. Cax bujuch c' åbech cax bujuch oquech soc a taquic a b åj soc m å' a bin tu ca werarex ich c'ac' munt q'uin yejer ca'tur a c' åb, bayiri' xan soc m å' a bin tu ca werarex ich c'ac' munt q'uin yejer ca'tur a woc. M å' ja wirej, ti' taro' u noq'uer b åc' m å' u quimin, m å' biq'uin a c'ac'o' u tupur.  
\v 47 Baxuc xan, a wichex. Wa raji' cu p åyic a si'pirex r åquej a wichex, jach manan tsoy ca' ocaquechex bujuch ichechex tu cu bin u reyintic C'uj wa quet yejer ca'tur a wichex cu bin u puriquechex ich tu cu yerar mac.  
\v 48 Tu y ån noc'or b åc' m å' u quimin, tu m å' u tupur a c'ac'o'. 
\p  
\v 49 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA  år åc'o' a cu sijic u winiquirob jud√≠o ti' C'uj tabta'an cu toquic ich c'ac'. Bayiri' xan, cu bin tumta'bir yor a mac a cu say år tin pach. Cu bin tumta'bir yor ten a mac a cu chuquic u pach a cu say år tin pacho'. Cu bin tumta'bir yor mac soc yiric wa taj cu yacsic tu yor.  
\v 50 Tsoy y ån u xa'anin, chen wa cu ruc'ur u xa'anin, m å' ch'o'ochi'. Taj ca c' åmejex u t' ån C'uj soc irechex xa'an. Ca' sisac a worex yejer a rac'obex. 
\c 10  
\s1 Jes√∫s cu camsic m å' tsoy u p' åtic u rac' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ19.1‚Äë12; Lc.‚ÄØ16.18) 
\p  
\v 1 Caj ruq'uij ti' taro' caj tar tu cu xur u ru'umin Judea caj u ch' åtaj ya'arir u c'aba' Jord√°n. A ya'ab macobe' caj u w åc' ås much'quintajob u b åj tu yicn ån Jes√∫s. Jeroj tune', caj u y ånxchun u w åc' ås camsic ti'ob an ten bic cu nanij u camsic ti'ob uch.  
\v 2 Caj c'uchob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yicn ån Jes√∫s, caj u chich c'atajob ti' quir u tumticob yor, wa tsoy turiri' mam u p' åtic u rac'.  
\v 3 Barej Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBa' yarm ån techex Mois√©s uch? 
\p  
\v 4 Robobe' caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïA Mois√©se' ara'b u ts'ibtej u ju'unin quir u p' åtic u rac'. Ca' bin ts'ocac u ts'ibtic u ju'unin jeroj tsoy u p' åtic. Baxuc ara'b ten Mois√©s. 
\p  
\v 5 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBarej caj u ts'ibtaj techex a ra' t' åno' caj u ts'ibtaj quire' caj u yiraj jach chich a jo'rex.  
\v 6 Barej u ch'ic chunin ber caj beta'b ich yoc'ocabe', ra' u q'uinin caj beta'b tu cotor a ba', caj ara'b ich u t' ån C'uj: ‚ÄúXib yejer xquic caj beta'b ten C'uj.‚Äù  
\v 7 ‚ÄúRajen juntur a xibe' bin u p' åtej u tet yejer u n å' quir u p'eriquintic u b åj yejer u rac'.  
\v 8 A ca'turo' ca'che' tu p'eri'quintaj u b åjob.‚Äù Rajen robob m å' ca'turobi' chen turiri' y ån.  
\v 9 Rajen a ba' p'eriquinta'b ten C'uj m å' tsoy u j åsic a xibo'. 
\p  
\v 10 Barej caj ocob ich naj u cams åwinicob caj tarob u c'aticob ti' ba' caj u camsaj ti'ob sam.  
\v 11 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïWa mac cu p' åtic u rac' quir u bin u ch'ic u jer, caj ts'oc u ch'ic u jer, y ån u si'pir, irej a mac a cu man yejer u jer xquic.  
\v 12 Wa ja xquico' cu p' åtic u mam quir u bin u ch'ic u jer, caj ts'oc u ch'ic u jer, y ån u si'pir, irej a xquico' a cu man yejer u jer xibo'. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu t' ånic C'uj ti' a chichano' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ19.13‚Äë15; Lc.‚ÄØ18.15‚Äë17) 
\p  
\v 13 Y ån mac caj tar purbir chichan ich Jes√∫s quir u ts'anc' åba'rob ten Jes√∫s soc u yamta'rob ten C'uj. Caj u t' ånej C'uj Jes√∫s quir u yamta'rob chichan ten C'uj. A y åjpurirob chichan ich Jes√∫s caj q'ueya'bob ten u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s.  
\v 14 C'uxij yor Jes√∫s caj u yiraj rajen caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïTsire'ej u tar purbir a chichano', ca' u yirenob. M å' a m åquex u berob quir u tarob ten. M å' ja wirej, a chichano' seb cu tar tu y ånen.  
\v 15 Wa mac u c'at u yocar tu cu bin u reyintejob C'uj arej u c ånejob a chichano'.  
\v 16 Jeroj tune', caj u ch'aj u mec'ob jujuntur a chichano' caj u ts'aj u c' åb yoc'orob jujuntur a chichano' caj u t' ånaj C'uj soc u yamta'rob ten C'uj a chichano'. 
\s1 A m å' uch xuruc u baquer xib a ney ån u taq'uin 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ19.16‚Äë30; Lc.‚ÄØ18.18‚Äë30) 
\p  
\v 17 A ray u q'uinino' cu joc'ar Jes√∫s quir u bin tu bej, caj tar yacab yicn ån Jes√∫s turiri' mac, caj xonraj  åc åtan caj u c'ataj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïJach tsoyech in w åjcams åy åjirech. Arej ten ba' ca' in betej soc in cuxtar munt q'uin? 
\p  
\v 18 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' a xibo': 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin ca wa'aric tsoyen? M åna' mac jach tsoy chen jari' C'uj tsoyo'.  
\v 19 Tech a wer ba' caj u ts'ibtaj Mois√©s uch: ‚ÄúM å' a y ån man yejer xquic, baxuc xquic m å' u y ån man yejer xib. Baxuc xan, m å' ja quinsic mac. Baxuc xan, m å' a wa'cric ba'. Baxuc xan, m å' a y ån tusic mac. Baxuc xan, m å' a y ån tusaric ba'. Y ån s åj ta tet yejer a n å' xan.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Raji' tune', caj u nuncaj, caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcamsay åjirech, tu cotor aro' caj in toc quibaj tin chich ånin uch. 
\p  
\v 21 Jes√∫s tune', caj u p åctaje' caj u yajquintaj, caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïY ån turiri' ba' m å' ta quibaj, ca' a betej aro'. Canej tu cotor a ba' y ån tech. Cu ts'ocar a r åc canic, ca' a j åsej a taq'uin ti' a mac otsiro'. Cu ts'ocar aro' ca' taquech tin pach quir a c ånic in t' ån, cax wa je' a quimin. Ca' bin c'uchuquech ich ca'anan, cu bin ts'ab år tech a ba' jach co'ojo'. 
\p  
\v 22 Caj ts'oc yubic a ba' caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' caj tucurn åjij quire' jach y ån u taq'uin. Caj bine', yajij yor. 
\p  
\v 23 Jes√∫s tune', caj sut u b åj caj pacatn åjij caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob: 
\p ‚ÄïJach yaj yocar mac a ney ån u taq'uine' tu cu reyinticob C'uj. 
\p  
\v 24 Caj jac' yorob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s quire' a ray t' åno' a ba' caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s. Jeroj tune', caj u w åc' ås araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïIn pararechex, jach yaj yocar mac a ney ån u taq'uine' tu cu reyinticob C'uj quire' u yaj u taq'uin.  
\v 25 Je' wa ju c'uchur yor yocar y år åc' tsimin ich u jorir yit' puts'? M å' u c'uchur yor quire' chichin u jorir yit' puts'. Je' wa ju c'uchur yor ocar ich ca'anan a mac a ne y ån u taq'uin? M å' u yocar quire' u yaj u taq'uin. Jaj ix t åcoj, je' u yocar y år åc' tsimin ich u jorir u yit' puts'. Chen a mac a neyan u taq'uin m å' ju yocar tu cu bin u reyintejob C'uj quire' u yaj u taq'uin. 
\p  
\v 26 Caj u yubajob u cams åwinicob caj jaq'uij yorob caj u pacran c'atajob ich u yet cams åwinicob: 
\p ‚ÄïA mac cu bin tacbir ten C'uj tun? 
\p  
\v 27 Jes√∫s caj pacta'bob caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïA xibo' m å' c'ucha'an yor u taquic u b åj, chen C'uj c'ucha'an yor u taquic tu cotor mac, quire' C'uj c'ucha'an yor ti' tu cotor ba'. 
\p  
\v 28 Pedro tune', caj u y ånxchun ya'aric ti': 
\p ‚ÄïJaj Ts'urir biquinin a ney ån u taq'uin m å' u r åc p' åtaj a ba' y ån ti' quir u say ta pach quir u c ånic a t' ån? A tenob caj in r åc p' åtajob a ba' y åntenob caj sayenob ta pach quir in c ånicob a t' ån. An ba' cu bin u ts'ic tenob C'uj, quire' caj in toc r åc p' åtajob a ba' y ån tenob uch? 
\p  
\v 29 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïJach taj quin wa'aric techex. A mac a caj u p' åtaj yatoch tu cotor, cax u w åc' ås u b åjob, cax u w åc' ås tet, cax u n å', cax wa ju pararob, cax wa ju ru'umin quir u yamtiquen yejer u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj.  
\v 30 A mac a caj u p' åtaj aro' cu bin u c' åmej ti' C'uj a ba' jach tsoyo' tu q'uinin baje'rer, jach manan cu bin ts'ab år ti'. Cu bin ts'ab år yatochob. Cu bin ts'ab år ti' u ru'umob. Ra'iri' u q'uinin xan, je' u chuquicob u pach quire' caj u yacsaj tu yor in t' ån. Baxuc xan, ca' bin xuruc t' ån, je' u ts'ab år ti' u cuxtar munt q'uin.  
\v 31 Barej ya'ab a ra' y ån p åybeje' baje'rer, cu bin man pachir cu man u ts'ati' pachir p åybeji'. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu w åc' ås aric bin u caj quimin 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ20.17‚Äë19; Lc.‚ÄØ18.31‚Äë34) 
\p  
\v 32 Jes√∫s cu bin ich u berir Jerusal√©n, yet binacob ya'ab macob. Jes√∫s p åybej cu bin. Jac'a'an yorob cu binob a yet binacob, a cu say årob tu pache' caj saj åcch åjob. Jeroj tune', tu junanob caj u p åyaj u cams åwinicob quire' u tsicb åtic ti'ob u docejob. Caj u y ånxchun u ya'aric ti'ob a ba' cu bin tar ti' ca' bin c'uchucob tu cajar Jerusal√©n: 
\p  
\v 33 ‚ÄïIric quic binex tu cajar Jerusal√©n. Ti' cu bin u quinsiquenob. Ti' cu y ån bin u c'ubiquenobi' ti' u jach ts'urirob sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o, yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s. Robob cu bin ya'arejob ca' quinsaquen, a teno' a baxuquenechexe'. M å' ja wirej, cu bin u c'ubiquenob xan ti' a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠o.  
\v 34 Robob bin u p'astiquenob, bin u j åts'enob, bin u tubiquenob, jeroj tune', bin u quinsenob. M åna' u nup u q'uinin ca' bin riq'uiquen ti' in quimirir. 
\s1 A ba' u c'atob Jacobo yejer Juan 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ20.20‚Äë28) 
\p  
\v 35 Jacobo tun, yejer Juan, u pararob Zebedeojo' caj tarob tu yicn ån Jes√∫s, caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcamsay åjirechob, wa quin c'aticob ba' ti' tech, in c'atob ca' a betej ti' a tenob. 
\p  
\v 36 Raji' tune', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBa' a c'atex ca' in betej techex? 
\p  
\v 37 Robob caj u ya'arajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïArej tenob ca' curaquenob turiri' ta noj bayiri' turiri' ta ts'ic ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin ca' ocaquech tu cu reyinticob C'uj a mac tu cotor. 
\p  
\v 38 Jes√∫s tune', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA techexo', m å' a werex ba' ca c'atiquex ten. Arex ten wa c'ucha'an a worex a muc'yajex an ten bic ca' bin muc'yajn åquen ich cruz? Bayiri' xan, arex ten wa c'ucha'an a worex a muc'yajex an ten bic ca' bin muc'yajn åquenob ti' a macob? 
\p  
\v 39 Robob caj u ya'arajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïC'ucha'an in worob in muc'yajob an bic tech. 
\p Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p  
\v 40 ‚ÄïTaj quin wa'aric. Je' a muc'yajex an bic ten. Chen m å' c'ucha'an in wor in curquintiquechex ich in noj m å' ich in ts'ic quire' m å' ten y ånin. Quire' in Tet C'uj y ånin quir u curquintic mac u c'at C'uj. Raji' u y ån ricsm ån uch. 
\p  
\v 41 Barej caj yubob a diezo' u yet cams åwinicob a ba' c'ata'b ti' Jes√∫s ten Juan yejer Jacobo. U yet cams åwinicob caj p'ujob yejer Juan yejer Jacobo.  
\v 42 Barej Jes√∫s caj u t' ånaj ca' u much'quintejob u b åj u cams åwinicob quir u camsic, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA werex a mac u jach ts'urirob u cajarob a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠o, cu jach ts'uririnticob u winiquirob. Bayiri' xan, cu naj ts'uririnticob u winiquirob quir u beticob a ba' u c'atob u jach ts'urirob.  
\v 43 M å' a y ån c åniquex a baxuc u jach ts'urirob a m å' u winiquirob jud√≠o, a mac u c'at u ts'uririnticob u yet acsa'orirob. Arej ca' u yamtej u yet cams åwinicob.  
\v 44 Cax a mac ich techex u c'at u ts'uririntic u yet cams åwinicob, arej ca' u yamtej u yet cams åwinicob soc irej u c'urew. 
\p  
\v 45 Caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïCa' a c åniquenex, a teno' a baxuquenechex. M å' taren quir u yamtiquenob. Taren in yamtic tu cotor mac. Taren quir in quinsa'r soc in r åc bo'otic u bo'orir ca' siptacob u binob u si'pirob ya'ab mac. 
\s1 Jawsa'b u wich Bartimeo ten Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ20.29‚Äë34; Lc.‚ÄØ18.35‚Äë43) 
\p  
\v 46 Caj tarob tu cajar Jeric√≥. Quire' cu joc'ar ich u cajar Jeric√≥ yet binacob u cams åwinicob yejer xan p'enc åch ya'ab macob, ti' cura'an a ch'op u wiche' ich n åc' bej. Cu c'atic u taq'uin quir u jan ån. Bartimeo u c'aba' a ch'op u wiche', raji' u parar Timeo.  
\v 47 Barej caj u yubaj Jes√∫s a cu tar tu cajar Nazaret caj mane' caj u y ånxchun u yaw åt caj ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïJes√∫s, u pararech a nunquir u rey David, chan yajquin ten. 
\p  
\v 48 Q'ueya'b ten ya'ab mac ca' u m åc u chi'. Barej raji' caj u jach c'amquintic aw åt: 
\p ‚ÄïU pararech a nunquir u rey David chan yajquin ten. 
\p  
\v 49 Jes√∫s caj xurij ich bej caj u p åyaj a ch'op u wiche'. Caj u p åyajob a pimo' ti' a ch'op u wiche', caj ya'arob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïChichquintej a wor, riq'uen cu t' åniquech ‚Äïquij ya'ara' ten a pimo'. 
\p  
\v 50 Bartimeo tune', caj ric' caj u pitaj u ca' ya'arir u noq'ue', caj u ch'aj u sit', caj tarij yicn ån Jes√∫s.  
\v 51 Caj t' ån ten Jes√∫se', caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïBa' a c'at ten quir in yamtiquech? 
\p A Bartimeojo' caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åj cams åy åjirech ca' sasich åj åc in wich soc ch åca'an in wiric in ber. 
\p  
\v 52 Caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti': 
\p ‚ÄïXen, quire' caj a wacsaj ta wor ten, jaw a wich. Seb caj jaw u wich, caj pacatn åjij, caj bin tu pach Jes√∫s ich bej. 
\c 11  
\s1 Jes√∫s ti' oquij ich u cajar Jerusal√©n 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.1‚Äë11; Lc.‚ÄØ19.28‚Äë40; Jn.‚ÄØ12.12‚Äë19) 
\p  
\v 1 Barej caj nats'ob tu cajar Jerusal√©n, caj y ån c'uchob u chan cajar u c'aba' Betfag√© quet yejer u chan cajar Betania. Jach bayt åc tu y ån u chan p'uc witsir u c'aba' Olivos quire' ti' p åca'an u p åc'ar ich u cor u che'er Olivos. Jes√∫s caj u tuchi'taj ca'tur u cams åwinicob ca' xicob.  
\v 2 Caj ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïXenex ich u chan cajar c' ås bayt åc. Ca' bin ocaquechex ich u cajar je' a wiriquex chan tsimin ti' maca'an, m åna' mac naca'an c åptar u c åpm ån tu pach. Pitex ca' a p åyex tera'.  
\v 3 Wa mac cu c'atic techex: ‚ÄúBiquinin ca pitiquex chan tsimin?‚Äù Y ån are baxuc a jera': Quire' ic Jaj Ts'urir u c'at u c åptar tu pach, quechex ti'. Ca' bin tsocac u c' ånique' seb cu w åc' ås tuchi'tej tera'. 
\p  
\v 4 Caj binob ca'tur u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj u yirajob a chan tsinino' ti' maca'an tancab bayt åc tu y ån u jor a najo'. Tu ber y ån. Jeroj tune', caj u pitajob a chan tsimino'. 
\p  
\v 5 Jun yarob ti' a macob, a ti' tar y ånobob, caj u c'atajob ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBa' ca betex? Biquinin ca pitiquex a chan tsimino'? 
\p  
\v 6 Robob tune', caj u ya'arajob ti'ob quire' ara'bob ten Jes√∫se', caj cha'aj ti'ob chan tsimin.  
\v 7 A ca'tur u cams åwinicob caj u paytajob chan tsimin, caj binob u purej ich Jes√∫s, caj u j åyajob noc' tu pach chan tsimin. U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj u yamtajob Jes√∫s quir u c åptar tu pach chan tsimin.  
\v 8 Ya'ab mac cu j åyicob uch u ca' yarir u noc'ob te' ich bejo' tu cu man y år åc' chan tsimin an ten bic rey cu c'uchur tu cajar. U jer jun yarob caj u ch' åcajob u c' åb che' caj u j åyajob te' ich bej xan, a baywo' cu yesicob cu s åjticob a mac a cu tar ich bej. 
\p  
\v 9 A mac a cu bin p åybej ti' Jes√∫s yejer a ra' cu tarob tu pach, caj c'ay ån åjob tu cu ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïJach caremech C'uj. C'uj caj a yamtaj a mac a cu tar tu c'aba' Jaj Ts'ur. Ca' ij carex Hosanna.  
\v 10 Jach manan tsoy wa macob cu qui' t' ånticob tu cu bin u reyinticob u rey ic nunquirex David a cu bin tar. Ca' ij carex Jach caremech C'uj. 
\p  
\v 11 Caj oc Jes√∫s tu cajar Jerusal√©n. Barej caj oc Jes√∫s tu carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, caj u r åc p åctaj tu cotor a ba' ti' y åno'. Jeroj tune', caj joc' quir u bin tu cajar Betania yejer u docejo' u cams åwinicob quire' cu bin q'uin. 
\s1 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti': M å' a wich ånc år u che'er higo 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.18‚Äë19) 
\p  
\v 12 Caj sasij, jeroj tune', caj joc'ob tu cajar Betania, caj wi'ijch åjij.  
\v 13 Caj u yiraj nach turiri' u che'er higo, y ån u re', rajen caj u juts' u b åj Jes√∫s yirej wa jix ti' y ån u wich, caj yiraj m åna' u wich chen u re' y ån, quire' m å' ra' u q'uinin u wich ån åc år.  
\v 14 Jeroj tune', caj u t' ånaj, Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïM å' biq'uin ca' bin mac' åc a wich ten mac ‚Äïquij ya'ara' ti' u che'er higo. 
\p Caj u'ya'b ten u cams åwinicob. 
\s1 Joc'sa'b a mac cu naj conanob ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.12‚Äë17; Lc.‚ÄØ19.45‚Äë48; Jn.‚ÄØ2.13‚Äë22) 
\p  
\v 15 Barej caj urob tu cajar Jerusal√©n tiri' caj oquij Jes√∫s ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Caj u y ånxchun u joc'sic a mac a cu canicob u ba'tac tu japnin carem naj, bayiri' xan, a mac cu m ånicob, caj u r åc j åw åcch'intej Jes√∫s u poche'ir tu cu c'axicob u taq'uin, bayiri' xan, caj u r åc j åw åcch'intej u cutanob tu cu canic u y år åc' susuy.  
\v 16 M å' cha'b u ch'a'acob ba' ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o.  
\v 17 Caj u camsaj ti'ob, tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' wa c'aj techex tub ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj tu cu ya'aric C'uj: ‚ÄúA jera' u najir quir u yocar mac u t' ånic C'uj, cax tu cotor mac tu cu tarob tu cajarob ich tu cotor u ru'umirob‚Äù; chen a techexo' caj a waysajex irej u japnin tunich tu cu naj tar a mac a cu ya'cricob ba'. 
\p  
\v 18 Barej caj u'ya'b ten u jach ts'urirob tu cotor u sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s caj u c åxtob bic tabar u quinsicob. Quire' tu cotor macob jac'a'an yorob ti' a ba' cu camsic, rajen robob, u jach ts'urirob tu cotor sacerdote yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s caj u ch'aj saquirob ti' Jes√∫s.  
\v 19 Barej ber cu bin q'uin, caj joc'ob tu cajar Jerusal√©n caj bin Jes√∫s quet yejer u cams åwinicob. 
\s1 Tijij u che'er higo 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.20‚Äë22) 
\p  
\v 20 A'acbir samam caj manob caj u yirajob r åc tijij u che'er higo tac tu mots.  
\v 21 Caj c'ajij yic' Pedro, caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech, iric quimij a ray u che'er higo a ta ro'ro' t' åntaj, caj r åc tijij u che'er. 
\p  
\v 22 Caj u nuncaj Jes√∫se', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïCa' acsex ta worex ti' C'uj.  
\v 23 Taj quin wa'aric techex, je' u c'uchur a worexe' a t' ånex cax a je' witsa' ca' xic ich u chi'c'ac'nab, je' u bine' wa ca wacsiquex ta worex, wa ta worex m å' a wa'ariquex: ‚ÄúJe' wa ju bine' wa quin wac ti'.‚Äù M å' ja wirej, je' u bine' quire' caj a wacsajex ta worex je' u bine'.  
\v 24 Rajen, quin wa'aric techex, wa ber ca t' åniquex C'uj ti' a ba' a c'atex, acsej ta worex wa bin a c' åmiquex jeroj tune' bin tac ti' techex tu cotor a ba' caj a c'atajex ti' C'uj.  
\v 25 Wa ber ca t' åniquex C'uj ca' a pacran jawsex u si'pir a ca tucriquex wa mac caj u betaj c'as ti' techex soc a Tetex ca'anan ca' u jawsej a si'pirex xan.  
\v 26 Quire' wa techex m å' ja jawsiquex u si'pirob bayiri' xan a Tetex a ti' y ån ich ca'anano' m å' u bin u jawsic a si'pirex xan. 
\s1 Mac ts'a'b u beyaj ti' Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.23‚Äë27; Lc.‚ÄØ20.1‚Äë8) 
\p  
\v 27 Caj c'uchij Jes√∫s ich u cajar Jerusal√©n yejer u cams åwinicob. Quire' cu man ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, caj u juts'ob u b åj u jach ts'urirob tu cotor sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s yejer u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o a Nuxibe'. Caj u juts'ob u b åj ich Jes√∫s caj c'atab ti' Jes√∫s.  
\v 28 Caj u ya'arajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïMac caj u ya'araj tech ca' a joc'sej jo'oraj? Tub u tar a muc' quir a jawsic mac? Tub u tar a muc' quir a camsic mac? Mac caj u ts'aj a muc'? 
\p  
\v 29 Caj nuncaj Jes√∫se', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc techex xan, je' in c'atic techex wa taj ca nunquiquex ten je' in wa'aric techexe' tub u tar in muq'ue' quir in betic aro'.  
\v 30 Arex ten ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. Mac tuchi'tej Juan quir u yacsic ja' tu jo'r mac. C'uj wa tuchi'tej wa xib tu tuchi'taj? 
\p  
\v 31 Caj ts'oc yubicob a ba' c'ata'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s, cu pacran nunquicob u t' ån ich u b åjiri'ob tan ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïWa quij cariquex ti': ‚ÄúC'uj tuchi'tej‚Äù, je' u ya'aric to'onex: ‚ÄúBiquinin m å' ta quibex u t' ån Juan uch?‚Äù  
\v 32 Barej wa quij cariquex ti': ‚ÄúA Juano' tuxta'b ten xib‚Äù, quic s åjtiquex a ya'ab macob quire' robob cu tucricob tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj rajen yerob jach jaj Juane' a mac ts'a'b u tucuric ten C'uj quir u tsicbar a ba' u c'at C'ujo'. 
\p  
\v 33 Caj u nucajob, caj u ya'arajob ti' Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' in werob mac tuchi'tej Juan. 
\p Baxuc caj w åc' ås nunca'b ten Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc xan, m å' in wa'aric tub u tar in muc' a ba' quin betic. 
\c 12  
\s1 Y åjcarirob u corir uva 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ21.33‚Äë46; Lc.‚ÄØ20.9‚Äë19) 
\p  
\v 1 Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun u camsic a ya'ab macob, caj u camsaj baxuc a jera' soc yerob a mac a m å' u c'at yacsic u yor quire' bin u caj ich c'ac'. Rajen caj u camsaj a jera': 
\p ‚ÄïTi' y ån mac cuch caj ts'oc u ch' åquic u che'er u cor, caj u r åc tocaj u robirir, caj u p åc'aj u yaq'uir uva. Caj ts'oc u p åq'uic caj u pa'te'taj u cor, caj u ts' åpquintaj tunich quir u ch'ictar ca'anan soc u c ånantic u wich uva soc m å' u r åc m åq'uicob ch'ich'. 
\p ‚ÄôCaj ya'araj u c ånata'rob u cor ten u winiquirob, quire' bin u caj nachir.  
\v 2 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u t'aquicob u wich uva u jach ts'urir caj u tuchi'taj u c'urew turiri' quir u c'atic u bo'orir tu tu t'acajob u wich uva ti' u y åjcarirob u corir uva. Quire' ca' u j åsob ti u ts'urirob u bo'orir u cor u ts'urir.  
\v 3 Caj chuc j åts'bir ten y åjcarirob u corir uva caj w åc' ås tuchi'ta'b ich u ts'urir, m åna' ba' ts'a'b ti'.  
\v 4 Tu w åc' ås tuchi'taj u jer u c'urew, barej caj u ch'inajob u jo'r, caj u buj åtstajob u yot'er u jo'r, toc cheta'b ten y åjcarirob u corir uva caj w åc' ås tuchi'ta'b ten y åjcarirob u corir uva ich u jach ts'urir.  
\v 5 Caj w åc' ås tuchi'taj u jer raji' xan caj u quinsajob. Bayiri' xan yejer u jerob ya'ab, jun yarob caj u b åb åj åtstajob, jun yarob caj u quinsajob. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄôTi' toy y ån uch turiri' u parar ich yicn ån u jach ts'urir, u jach yaj u parar. Jari' m åna' u jer mac quir u tuchi'tic, rajen caj u tuchi'taj u parar. Yer u jach ts'urir je' u s åjta' u parar ten y åjcarirob u corir uva.  
\v 7 Caj c'uchij u parar caj irir ten y åjcarirob u corir uva caj u pacran arajob ich u yet carirob u corir uva: ‚ÄúRaji' u parar ic jach ts'urirex cu tar. Raji' cu bin ch'ic u cor wa cu quimin u tet. Ca' xico'onex ij quinsex u parar soc to'onex quic bin ic ch'iquex u cor.‚Äù  
\v 8 Caj u chucajob ca' xicob u quinsejob ich u n åc' c'axir u cor. Ti' tu jach quinsajob ich u n åc' c'axir u cor, caj u pich'intajob u baquer. 
\p  
\v 9 Jes√∫s caj u c'ataj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïArex ten, ba' cu bin u betic u jach ts'urir u cor ti' y åjcarirob u corir uva ca' bin tac? Je' u tar u jach ts'urir quir u joc'sic u quinsej quir u ts'ic ti' u jerob mac. 
\p  
\v 10 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti' u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' wa ja xacm ånex a ts'iba'an u t' ån C'uj a jera': 
\q1 U yoc naj a caj u pich'intajob y åjc' åxirob naj quire' m å' u c'atobi'. A jera' yoc naj a caj u purob m åna' u jer jach chich u muc'. Chen caj u w åc' ås chucob quir u c' åxicob naj soc u chichtar u muc'.  
\v 11 A jera' caj beta'b ten C'uj. M å' wa cu jac'ar ij corex ij quiriquex? 
\p  
\v 12 Caj najta'bir ten u jach ts'urirob tu cotor u winiquirob jud√≠o a ba' camsa'b ti'ob sam ra' quir u najticob rajen caj u tumtajob u tuchi'ticob chucbir Jes√∫s. Quire' cu s åjticob a pimob rajen p'at, rajen binob. 
\s1 Tar c'ata'bir ti' u bo'orir gobierno 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ22.15‚Äë22; Lc.‚ÄØ20.20‚Äë26) 
\p  
\v 13 Caj u tuchi'tajob jun yarob u winiquirob jud√≠o a fariseojo' yejer u cams åwinicob Herodes ti' Jes√∫s quir u tus wayticob u t' ån soc u tus taquicob u jo'r ich gobernador.  
\v 14 Barej caj tarob caj u ya'arajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirechob ‚Äïquij‚Äï, in werob taj a ba' ca wac. Baxuc taj a ba' ca camsic ti' u t' ån C'uj. M å' a coyen ca chich aric ti' mac, quet ca wa'aric ti'ob. Quire' baxuc taj ca camsic tenob a ba' u c'at C'uj ti' a tenob. Arej tenob quire' in c'atob in werob wa tsoy in bo'oticob in ru'umob ti' rey? Wa m å' tsoy in bo'oticob in ru'umob ti' rey? 
\p  
\v 15 Jes√∫s yer a ba' c'as cu tucricob tu yorob caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin tarechex a tumtiquex in wor? Esej ten turiri' a taq'uinex ca' in wirej. 
\p  
\v 16 Caj u yesajob ti' Jes√∫s. Raji' caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïMac jot'a'an u yo'ochir? Mac u c'aba' ts'iba'an ti'? 
\p Caj u ya'arajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïRa' u yo'ochir u rey C√©sar, jot'a'an ich s åc taq'uin. 
\p  
\v 17 Caj u ya'araj Jes√∫s ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïTaj a ba' ca wa'ariquex. Rajen ca' a quibex a ba' cu ya'aric techex u rey C√©sar, baxuc xan, ca' a quibex a ba' a cu ya'aric C'uj ti' techex. 
\p Chan jac'a'an yorob a ba' yubajob ya'aric Jes√∫s. 
\s1 Tar c'ata'bir bic tabar mac cu riq'uir tu quimirir 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ22.23‚Äë33; Lc.‚ÄØ20.27‚Äë40) 
\p  
\v 18 Baxuc xan, tarob u winiquirob jud√≠o a saduceojo'. Aro' cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúM å' u riq'uir mac tu quimirir.‚Äù Caj tarob u c'atej ba' ti' Jes√∫s caj ya'arajob ti' Jes√∫s: 
\p  
\v 19 ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirechob ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ic nunquirirex Mois√©s caj u ts'ibtaj to'onex uch a ba' ca' ic betejex caj u ya'araj wa ju mam cu quimin, cu p'at år u rac', m åna' u parar yejer, caj quimij u mam tu junan. Caj u ya'araj Mois√©s, ra' u yits'in u mam, raji' cu bin u ch'ic u raq'uintej u mu'. Soc yiric wa je' u parar ånc år yejer soc u ch'isic u parar, irej wa ju tus parar u sucu'un uch.  
\v 20 A sucu'unbiro' y ån seis yits'inob. A sucu'unbiro', raji' tu y ån ch'aj u rac', hasta u quimij m åna' u parar.  
\v 21 A its'inbiro', raji' caj u tacaj u chuch u sucu'un. Raji' caj u ch'aj u rac' u sucu'un, m åna' u parar xan caj quimij, a jach ca' its'inbiro', raji' caj u tacaj u chuch u ca' sucu'un. Raji' caj u ch'aj u rac' u ca' sucu'un. M åna' u parar xan.  
\v 22 Hasta nup u r åc ch'ic u yits'in u mam, hasta r åc quiminob m åna' u parar, caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u quimin a xquico', caj quimij.  
\v 23 Ca' bin riq'uic tu quimirir, mac cu bin u ch'ic u raq'uintej quire', siete tu ch'aj u mam? 
\p  
\v 24 Jes√∫s tune', caj u nuncaj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïM å' wa ja w åc' ås b åjiri'ex ca tusariquex quire' m å' ja najtex a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj bayiri' xan, m å' a werex wa jach chich u muc' C'uj.  
\v 25 Quire' ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u w åc' ås riq'uir mac ti' u quimirir, a xibo' m å' u raq'uintej xquic. Bayiri' a xquico' m å' u m åmintej xib quire' u jer cu bin waysa'bir ten C'uj robob irej y åjt' ånirob C'uj ca'anan.  
\v 26 Soc a c åniquex ba' u c'at ya'aric, je' u riq'uir mac ti' quimirir. Y ån c'aj techex tub ts'iba'an u t' ån C'uj. Caj ya'araj C'uj ti' Mois√©s ich a ray chan che'er a erar u ca' uch an bic C'uj cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúTu c'ujinten Abraham uch, bayiri' Isaac yejer Jacob.‚Äù  
\v 27 A C'ujo' m å' quimen yiric a nunquirex, cuxa'an yiric a C'ujo'. M å' ja wirej, cuxa'an yiric a C'ujo' tu cotor mac. Rajen m å' qui'jij a waquex. 
\s1 Te'en u t' ån ich u t' ån C'uj a jach no'ojo' 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ22.34‚Äë40) 
\p  
\v 28 Caj u juts'aj u b åj turiri' ich Jes√∫s, y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s a mac caj u yubaj uch bic cu nunquicob u t' ån Jes√∫s a saduceojo'. Tsoy caj u yubaj u nunquic Jes√∫s ti' u pacran t' ånob, caj u c'ataj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïArej ten a jach manan tsoyir u t' ån C'uj ich tu cotor ca' in quibejob. 
\p  
\v 29 Jes√∫s tune' caj u nuncaj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïA jera' a jach manan tsoyir u t' ån C'uj ich tu cotor: ‚ÄúU'yex tu cotor u winiquirechex israel a Jaj Ts'uro', raji' ij C'ujirex, jari' raji' ic Jaj Ts'urirex.  
\v 30 Yajquintej C'uj, quire' raji' a Jaj Ts'urirex. Qui' yajquintej C'uj yejer tu cotor a pixam, yejer tu cotor a muc' yejer tu cotor a wor xan‚Äù, quire' raji' p åybej ich u t' ån C'uj. Rajen ca' a qui' quibex a jera'.  
\v 31 Quet bayiri' ti' y ån u jer a cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúYajquintej a rac'ob an bic ca w åc' ås yajquintic a b åjiri're'.‚Äù M åna' u jer tu ts'iba'an ich u t' ån a jach manan noj ti' aro'. 
\p  
\v 32 A y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s tuno', caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïJach taj caj a wa'araj ten, in w åjcams åy åjirech, caj a wa'araj jach taj, turiri' C'uj y ån, m åna' u jer, jariro'.  
\v 33 Taj caj a wa'araj ca' ic yajquintex C'uj yejer tu cotor ic pixamex yejer tu cotor ic tucurex yejer tu cotor ic muq'uex, bayiri' xan, ca' ic yajquintex ic rac'obex an bic ic w åc' ås b åjex ic yajquintiquex, a jera' a caj a wa'araj jach manan ti' tu cotor a ba'  år åc'a'an a cu toquic quir u sijic ti' C'uj, bayir' ti' tu cotor a ba' cax cu sijicob ti' C'uj. 
\p  
\v 34 Jes√∫s caj u toc u'yaj tsoy an bic caj u nuncaj ti' a y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s quire' caj u nuncaj an bic caj u najtaj a ba' ara'b ti' ten Jes√∫s. Rajen caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïTabar a wocar tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj. 
\p Jeroj tune', caj p'atob u tar u c'aticob ba' ti' Jes√∫s, saj åcob u c'atej. 
\s1 A Cristojo' u ch'ic parar u nunquir David 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ22.41‚Äë46; Lc.‚ÄØ20.41‚Äë44) 
\p  
\v 35 Barej ti' y ån Jes√∫s ich a carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o tu cu camsic caj u c'ataj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBic tabar cu ya'aric a y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s wa Cristo raji' u ch'ic ca' parar u nunquir David?  
\v 36 Arex ten biquinin David caj u t' ånaj: ‚ÄúIn Jaj Ts'urir‚Äù ‚Äïquij David. M å' ja wirej caj yamta'b ten u Taj'or u Pixam C'uj caj u ts'ibtaj a jera': 
\q1 A C'ujo' caj u ya'araj ti' in Jaj Ts'urir, quij ya'aric David: ‚ÄúCuren tin noj, quij C'uj, hasta quin r åc ch'esic a mac a cu p'atiquech.‚Äù 
\m  
\v 37 Bic tabar Cristo u ch'ic ca' parar a nunquirex David wa David u b åj t' ånej: ‚ÄúIn Jaj Ts'urir‚Äù? Rajen ij querex a Cristojo' raji' m å' chen u ch'ic ca' parar a nunquirex David. 
\p A macob a ti' y ånob, quire' p'enc åch ya'ab ti' y ånob, jach tsoy tu xiquinob caj u yubajob ti'. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ta'quic u jo'r a y åjcams åy åjir u t' ån Mois√©s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ23.1‚Äë36; Lc.‚ÄØ11.37‚Äë54; 20.45‚Äë47) 
\p  
\v 38 Tu cu camsic Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïQui' c ånantechex a b åjex soc m å' a c åniquex a y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©se'. M å' ja wirej, u y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s jach c' år åp u noc' cu manob soc u tus tucricob u rac'ob jach noj aro'. Qui' yorob yiricob baxucob. Jach qui' yorob yiricob u t' ån ån ten u rac'ob tu cu naj bin u m ånicob yo'ochob quire' cu yiricob tus noj aro'.  
\v 39 Baxuc cu teticob u cutanob tu cu cutarob a jach no'ojo' tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj tu chan najirob. Baxuc tu cu qui'qui' jan ånob soc u tus irir jach nojob.  
\v 40 M å' ja wirej, a y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s cu tus aricob ti' a xquico' a quimenob u mamob soc u tus ts'ic yatoch yejer u ba'tac cax a ba' y ån tu yatochob. Robob jach ama'an cu ts'ocar u t' ånicob C'uj soc u rac'ob cu tus tucricob cu qui' c'ujinticob C'uj. Jach manan cu bin ts'abir u muc'yajob ten C'uj quire' cu beticob aro', cax yerob u t' ån C'uj. Chen u jer mac a m å' yerob C'uj m å' neyaj cu bin muc'yajob. 
\s1 U cuchir tu cu naj but'icob u taq'uinob 
\r (Lc.‚ÄØ21.1‚Äë4) 
\p  
\v 41 Quire' curucbar Jes√∫s  åc åtan ti' tu cuchir tu cu naj but'icob taq'uin tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Ra' taq'uin ti' carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj. Jes√∫s caj u yiraj cu but'icob ya'ab u taq'uin ya'ab mac, a ney ån u taq'uinob.  
\v 42 Caj u yiraj xan xquic, a quimen u mame', otsir, caj u but'aj u majan taq'uin, ca'tur ch åc taq'uin, a m å' coji'.  
\v 43 Jes√∫s tune', caj u t' ånaj ca' tacob u cams åwinicob tu yicn ån, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïTaj quin wa'aric techex, a je' xquica' a quimen u mame' cax otsir, chen caj u but'aj ca'tur ch åc taq'uin a m å' coji', chen  åc åtan tu wich C'uj coj caj u but'aj. Chen u rac'ob cax ya'ab caj u but'ajob, chen  åc åtan tu wich C'uj m å' coji'.  
\v 44 A mac a ne yan u taq'uinob caj u but'ajob u ta'quin tu cuchir tu cu naj but'icob u taq'uinob u winiquirob jud√≠o tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj. Quire' jach manan ya'ab caj u but'ajob quire' jach manan t'aj u taq'uinob, chen ra' caj u but'ob quire' m å' u r åc c' ånicobe' u taq'uin. Chen a xquico' a otsiro' caj u toc r åc but'aj ti'o' u ta'quin cax m åna' tu cu m ånic yo'och. 
\c 13  
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ya'aric bin u caj jubur carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ24.1‚Äë2; Lc.‚ÄØ21.5‚Äë6) 
\p  
\v 1 Quire' cu joc'ar Jes√∫s tu japnin carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Toc bin u caj uch, caj u juts'aj u b åj turiri' u cams åwinicob ich yicn ån Jes√∫s. Ca' ara'b ti': 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech, cha'antej biquira' a tunichob. M å' wa jach caremo'? Cha'antej biquira' a najobo' m å' jach carem xan? 
\p  
\v 2 Jes√∫s caj u nuncaj, caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïC' å'otej tech a je' carem naja' bic tabar caj a wiraji' quire' jach taj quin toc aric a wu'yej, ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin cu bin jubsa'bir. M å' u p'at tunich tub ts' åpa'an, m å' a bin a wirej ca'tur ts' åpa'an. Bin r åc jubucob a carem najobo'. 
\s1 A cu yesic tabar u xur t' ån 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ24.3‚Äë28; Lc.‚ÄØ21.7‚Äë24; 17.22‚Äë24) 
\p  
\v 3 Caj joc' Jes√∫s ich carem naj caj bin ich u jo'r chan p'uc witsir Olivos, Jes√∫s caj cur åj,  åc åtan ti' a carem najo' tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, quire' cu p åctic a carem najo', barej caj u juts'ob u b åj u cams åwinicob Pedro yejer Jacobo yejer Juan yejer Andr√©s soc tu junanob cu yubicob: 
\p  
\v 4 ‚ÄïTarenob in c'atob a toc aric tenob ber ca' bin jubsac carem naj? Biquira' carem naj ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin cu xur t' ån ca' bin urquech? 
\p  
\v 5 Caj nunca'b ti'ob ten Jes√∫s caj u y ånx chun u ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïQui' c ånantex a b åjex soc m åna' mac cu tar u tusaric techex, soc u p åyicob techex ca' a quibiquex a ba' cu tusaricob techex.  
\v 6 Quire' ya'ab mac cu bin tarob ich in c'aba', tan ya'aricob: ‚ÄúA teno' a Cristojeno'.‚Äù Rajen cu bin u beticob ca' a quibexob a ba' cu tusaricob techex.  
\v 7 Chen ber ca' bin a wu'yejex u juminta'rob: ‚ÄúTan u quinsicob u b åj ich u jer ru'um‚Äù, cax tu y ånechex xan, ca' bin u quinsicob u b åj. Je' a wu'yiquex tabar u quinsicob u b åj xan. Cax tan u manob u quinsicob u b åj, m å' a ch'aquex sajaquirex, quire' y ån u tar u quinsicob u b åj an ten bic u c'at C'uj. M å' toy c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur t' åni'.  
\v 8 Ra' u quinino' ca wu'yiquex cu ts'ictarob winiquirob ich jumpet ru'um. Cu bin u quinsicob u b åj yejer u winiquirob ich jumpet ru'um. Bayiri' xan, u ru'umin tu reyinta'b ten rey cu bin u quinsicob u b åj yejer u jer ru'um tu reyinta'b ten u jer rey. Bayiri', je' a wu'yiquex u pec ch'ic yum ru'umin ich u jerob ya'ab ru'umob. Bayiri' je' u wich åj årob xan ich jumpet ru'um, cax bayt åc cu bin u wich åj årob. Raji' u y ånx ch'ic chun u muc'yaj a cu bin tar ich yoc'ocab. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄôBarej a techexo' y ån c ånatechex a b åj. Quire' bin c'ubuquechex quir u tocar a jo'rex tu cu naj much'quinticob u b åj tu cotor u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o. Jeroj tune', bin u caj u j åts'icob a pachex ich u chan najir tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o. Ti' cu bin u chop åytiquechexob quir u bin u puriquechexob  åc åtan rey yejer ich gobernador quir u taquiquex a jo'rex quire' caj a wacsaj ta worex ti' ten, soc c'ucha'an a worex a wa'ariquex ba' u ber ti' techex.  
\v 10 M å' ja wirej, m å' toy c'uchuc tu q'uinin u xur a t' åno' u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj cu y ån bat'an tsec'ta'r ich tu cotor mac cax tu c åja'anob.  
\v 11 Ber ca' bin chucuquechex ca' c'ubuquechex  åc åtan a juezo' quir u taquiquex a jo'rex. M å' ja tucriquex ba' ca bin a wa'ariquex ti'ob, cax m å' toy xiquechex  åc åtan a mac a cu bin u taquiquex a jo'rex. Barej cu bin ts'abir techex a ray a q'uinino', ra' ca wa'ariquex quire' m å' techex ca t' ånexi' wa m å' a Taj'or u Pixam C'ujo'.  
\v 12 M å' chen a mac a cu p'actiquechex cu bin u chuquicob a pachex, a tet yejer a n å' cax a b åjob je' u c'ubiquechexob, baxuc je' u quinsiquechexob. Baxuc xan, u w åc' ås pararob cu bin u c'ubicob u tet yejer u n å' soc u quinsa'rob.  
\v 13 Quire' techex caj a wacsajex ta worex ten, tu cotor mac cu bin u p'actiquechexob, je' u ts'ab år techex a cuxtarex munt q'uin wa rajra' ca muc'tiquex a ba' cu tar techex tu cu chuquicob a pachex. 
\p  
\v 14 ‚ÄôM å' ja wirej, caj u ts'ibtaj Daniel a ts'ab u tucuric ten C'uj quir u ts'ibtic a ba' u c'at C'uj uch. Ra' caj u tsec'taj uch: ‚ÄúWa ber ca wiriquex a ba' jach c'as ch'ica'an ich u japanin carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o tu m å' tsoy u ch'ictaro' quire' m å' ra' u beyaj. Qui' tucriquex ‚Äïquij Daniel‚Äï, quire' raji' cu bin u c'asquintic u winiquirob Israel.‚Äù Jeroj tune', arej ti'ob a mac a ti' y ånob tu ru'umin Judea a ray u q'uinino' ca' puts'ucob ich wits.  
\v 15 A ray u q'uinino' wa ti' y ån mac tu jo'r yatoch tu taj u jo'r yatoch. Arex ti' m å' tsoy u yocar u ch'ic u ba'tac. Arex u toc puts'ur.  
\v 16 A ray u q'uinino' wa ti' y ån mac ich u cor. Arex m å' u sut u ch'ic u noc'.  
\v 17 A ray u q'uinino' jach otsirch åjij a xquico' a tabar u rochic u chan  år åc' ochir. Bayiri' a xquic a cu ts'ic chuch ti' chan  år åc' och.  
\v 18 A ray u q'uinino' t' ånex C'uj soc m å' ra' u q'uinin a puts'urex tu q'uinin que'er, quire' m å' a c'uchur a worex a muc'tiquex que'er.  
\v 19 Quire' a ray u q'uinino', jach manan cu bin muc'yajob a ra winiquirobo'. U jer winiquirob m å' u ne muc'yajob an ten bic cu bin u muc'yajob a ra winiquirobo' tu q'uinin cu bin xur t' ån. M å' biq'uin yubm ånobi' ra u q'uinin caj beta'b a ich yoc'ocabo' tu ch'ic chun uch. M å' ca' bin tac u jer u q'uinin a baxuco'.  
\v 20 A ray u q'uinino' wa Jaj Ts'ur u c'at u cha'ic u cochtar u pach q'uin soc ama'an cu bin muc'yajob a ra winiquirobo', m åna' mac cu bin p'at årob. Chen tabar u muc'yajob quire' ti' y ånob a mac a toc teta'b ten C'uj quire' yajbir ten C'uj. 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄôCa' bin c'uchuc a ray u q'uinino' wa mac cu bin ya'aric: ‚ÄúIrewirex, Cristo toc c'uchij quir u taquic mac tu cotor.‚Äù M å' a quibex a ba' cu ya'aricob. Cax cu ya'aricob: ‚ÄúA ray Cristojo'.‚Äù  
\v 22 Quire' a ray u q'uinino' ya'ab cu bin tarob quir u tusaricob ti' u rac'ob: ‚ÄúA teno' taren ich yoc'ocab quir in taquic mac, quire' tu tuchi'ten C'uj.‚Äù Tu cu tusaricob ti' mac je' u tus esicob carem beyaj xan. Cax a mac a teta'b ten C'uj orac u quibicob quire' cu tus iricob carem beyaj, quire' baxuc u c'atob, chen m å' u c'uchur u yorob ti'.  
\v 23 Quin toc aric techex a je' t' åna' soc a toc erex a ba' cu bin tar biq'uin soc m å' u jac' år a worex. 
\s1 Bic tabar ca' bin urac u parar C'uj 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ24.29‚Äë35, 42‚Äë44; Lc.‚ÄØ21.25‚Äë36) 
\p  
\v 24 Caj ya'araj Jes√∫s ti' u cams åwinicob: 
\p ‚ÄïA ray u quinino' a tabar u ts'ocar u muc'yaj a winiquirobo'. Je' u yac'birch åj år q'uine'. M å' u sasich åj år. Bayiri', ic n å' m å' u bin u ts'abir u sasirir.  
\v 25 A sa'abo', cu bin yiricob irej wa cu r åc rubur. Tu cotor ba' a ti' y ån ich ca'anano' cu cha'ic u pec C'uj.  
\v 26 Jeroj tune', cu bin yiricob in wu'ur a teno' a mac bayxuquenechexo'. Bin u yiriquenob quin tar tu muy årir yejer jach chich in muc', yejer u sasirir C'uj quin wu'ur.  
\v 27 Jeroj tune', bin tuchi'tac ten C'uj u y åjmasirob u t' ån quir u bin u much'quinta'rob a mac caj in tetajob ich yoc'ocab, cax tu y ånob, ti' cu bin u much'quinta'rob. 
\p  
\v 28 ‚ÄôC ånex a ba' cu camsico'onex che'er higuera. A werex cu jut'ur u re' che' quir u top' ånc år quire' cu yocar yaxq'uin, taj an ten bic aro'.  
\v 29 Bayiri' xan, ber ca wiriquex a ba' caj in camsajechex sam cu tar, jeroj tabar u xur t' ån.  
\v 30 C'aj techex a jera', quire' taj quin wa'aric techex. Ti' y ån mac baje'rer, ra' cu bin cuxtarob tac cu yiricob a ba' caj in toc araj techex cu tar ich tu y ånechex.  
\v 31 A ca'anano' je' u r åc ts'ocare', a je' ru'uma' je' u r åc ts'ocar xan. Chen in t' åno' m å' u bin ts'ocar quire' y ån u toc r åc nupur in t' ån ich yoc'ocab. 
\p  
\v 32 ‚ÄôChen ber cu bin tar a ba' caj in toc araj techex, m åna' mac yer ber u tar. Cax u y åjmasirob u t' ån C'uj, cax u parar C'uj m å' yer, chen u b åjiri' C'uj yer ber u tar. Rajen m åna' mac yer ber hora, cax ber u q'uinin m å' yer. 
\p  
\v 33 ‚ÄôQui' c ånatex a b åj, qui' p'iric a wichex ca' a t' ånejex C'uj soc m å' u nay år a worex. Quire' m å' a werex biq'uin quin tar ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï.  
\v 34 Aro' irej a xib a caj joc' quir u bin nachir. Caj u p' åtaj u yatoch, caj u ts'ajaj u muc' ti' u c'urewob, caj u j åsaj jujuntur u beyajob, caj u tuchi'taj a mac a cu c ånantic u jor yatoch tu cu naj ocar mac tu yatoch, caj ya'araj ti' ca' u qui' p'irej u wich soc yiric u yu'ur u jach ts'urir.  
\v 35 Qui' p'irej a wichex tun, quire' m å' a werex ber ca' bin tac u jach ts'urir a najo', wa jix ti' oq'uin cu yu'ur, wa jix ti' chumuc ac'bir cu yu'ur, wa jix ti' ca' bin c'ay ån åc cax cu yu'ur, wa jix ti' a'a'cbir cu yu'ur.  
\v 36 M å' ja wirej, wa jix ti' seb cu yu'ur ca' bin uruc jeroj cu yiric techex wen ån a ca'ex.  
\v 37 A ba' quin wa'aric techexa', quin wa'aric ti' tu cotor mac: ‚ÄúQui' p'irex a wichex.‚Äù 
\c 14  
\s1 Cu much'quinticob u tucurob u chuquejob Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.1‚Äë5; Lc.‚ÄØ22.1‚Äë2; Jn.‚ÄØ11.45‚Äë53) 
\p  
\v 1 Ca'bej cu c'uchur tu q'uinin u qui' qui' jan ånob u winiquirob jud√≠o. Ra' u q'uinin quir u c' å'oticob u potmasticob y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj uch, soc m å' u quiminob u parar xib a y ån rocha'b ten u n å'. Ra' u q'uinin xan, a pano' a m å' u sipe', quire' m å' p åji'. U jach ts'urirob u sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o yejer a y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©so' caj u c åxtob bic tabar u tusaricob ti' Jes√∫s soc u chuquicob u quinsicob Jes√∫s.  
\v 2 Robob caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' tu q'uinin u qui' qui' jan ånob a pascuajo'. Ca' ic y ån pajex u ts'ocar u quinin u qui' qui' jan ånob, soc m å' ic p'usiquex u yorob ij quet winiquirob jud√≠o a pimo'. 
\s1 Jes√∫s ich u cajar Betania 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.6‚Äë13; Jn.‚ÄØ12.1‚Äë8) 
\p  
\v 3 Quire' ti' y ån Jes√∫s ich u cajar Betania, curucbar tu jan ån tu yatoch Sim√≥n. Ra' u c ånm ån iq'uer u ca' uch. Jeroj tune', tarij turiri' xquic ich yatoch Sim√≥n yejer turiri' chan p'urir, chup yejer a ne qui' u boque', chen nardo u c'aba', a qui' u boque'. A nardojo', jach co'oj u bo'orir. A xquico' caj u pa'aj a chan p'uro' caj u wecaj a qui' u boque' tu jo'r Jes√∫s.  
\v 4 Yan jun yarob a ti' y ånob, caj p'ujob, caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïA biquinin caj u s åtaj a ra' qui' u boque' ich u jo'r Jes√∫s?  
\v 5 Wa caj u canaj ca'che' tu ca' jaraj u taq'uin quir u jas år ti' a jach otsirobo'. Quire' u bo'orir jach manij tres cientos s åc taq'uinob. 
\p Choc yorob ti' a xquico' quire' caj u xupaj a qui' u boque'. 
\p  
\v 6 Barej Jes√∫se' caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïTsire'ej, ba'wir ca ts'iquintex a xquico'. M å' ja wirej, caj u betaj tsoy ten, caj u jayaj tin jo'r a qui' u boque'.  
\v 7 A otsire', rajra' ti' y ån tu y ånechex an ber a c'atex, je' u c'uchur a worex a betiquex tsoy ti'ob, barej a teno' m å' rajra' ti' y ånen tub y ånechex.  
\v 8 A je' xquica', a ba' caj u betaj a ba' c'ucha'an yor ti', rajen caj u jayaj tin jo'r a qui' u boque', quire' tabar u muquicob in baquer.  
\v 9 Jach taj quin wa'ariquex tech ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï. Cax wa tu cu bin u tsec'tic u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj, je' ya'arique' bic caj u jayaj tin jo'r a xquico', a qui' u boque' soc u c' å'otic u c'aba' a je' xquica'. 
\s1 Judas cu bin c'ubic Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.14‚Äë16; Lc.‚ÄØ23.3‚Äë6) 
\p  
\v 10 Caj ts'oc yiric u joyar tu jo'r Jes√∫s a qui' u boque', caj bin Judas Iscariote quir u tsicbar yejer u jach ts'urirob sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o. Raji' turiri' ich doce u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s. Caj bin u c'ubic ti'ob.  
\v 11 Caj qui'jij yorob u jach ts'urirob sacerdote rajen caj u toc arajob je' u bo'ota' ten u jach ts'urir tu cotor u sacerdote quir u c'ubic Jes√∫s. Caj u y ånxchun u c åxtic bic tabar je' u c'ubique'. 
\s1 A oq'uin jan ån u q'uinin pascua 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.17‚Äë29; Lc.‚ÄØ22.7‚Äë23; Jn.‚ÄØ13.21‚Äë30; 1 Co. 11.23‚Äë26) 
\p  
\v 12 Caj c'uchij tu q'uinin u q'uinin a cu janticob yo'och pan a m å' u sipe'. Ra' u q'uinin xan, cu quinsicob y år åc' t åm ån yuc, chan ar soc u c' å'oticob bic C'uj caj u tacaj u nunquirirob u winiquirob jud√≠o ich u ru'umin Egipto. C'uch u cams åwinicob ich Jes√∫s caj u c'atajob ti': 
\p ‚ÄïArej tenob tub a c'at a jantej a wo'och oq'uin tu q'uinin u qui' qui' jan ånob u winiquirob jud√≠o? Arej tenob tub a c'at in ch åcob? 
\p  
\v 13 Caj u tuchi'taj ca'tur u cams åwinicob, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïXenex a je' cajaro', ti' ca bin a nupex tun, turiri' xib cu cuchic u p'urir u yo'och ja', sayenex tu pach.  
\v 14 Tu ca wiriquex tu cu yocar tu yatoch a ca' ts'ap yatocho', arex ti' u yumin a najo': ‚ÄúY åjcams åy ånireche' cu c'atic: Tu y ån u cuchir tu quin bin in jantejob a ba' cu naj janticob u winiquirob jud√≠o tu q'uinin pascua yejer in cams åwinicob?‚Äù  
\v 15 Raji'e' cu bin yesic techex junxot' yatoch u ca' tsap yatocho' toc y ån u pojche'ir tu cu jan ån. Toc y ån u cutan xan. Ti' taro' ca ch åquiquex ij co'ochex. 
\p  
\v 16 Caj binob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj yirajob an ten bic Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob, jeroj tune', caj ch åcajob yo'och quir u c' å'oticob u q'uinin pascua. 
\p  
\v 17 Barej caj ac'birch åjij, caj c'uchij Jes√∫s quir u jan ån. Yet tarac u doce u cams åwinicob.  
\v 18 Caj curajob tu jan ånob yejer Jes√∫s ich u pojche'ir yo'och. Cu jan ån Jes√∫s caj ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïJach taj quin wa'aric techex. Y ån turiri' ich techex, a docejo', a mac a p'eri' ic jan ånex, a cu bin u mucu c'ubiquene'. 
\p  
\v 19 Caj jach choquij yorob u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s. Jujuntur u cams åwinicob cu bin u c'aticob ti' Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïTen wa quin bin in c'ubiquech Jaj Ts'urir? 
\p  
\v 20 Raji' tune', caj u nuncaj, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA mac turiri' ich techex a docejo' a je' cu ruchic yo'och yejeren, raji' cu bin u c'ubiquen a ti' y ån yejerechex.  
\v 21 A teno' a baxuquenechexo', bin in ca' quinsbir, quire' tabar u nup'ur u t' ån C'uj. Chen otsir a mac a cu bin u mucu c'ubiquen a mac a tar soc u yamtic mac tu cotor. Jach manan tsoyir wa m å' ti' y ån tera' ich yoc'ocab. 
\p  
\v 22 Quire' tu cu jan ånobe', Jes√∫s caj u ch'aj yo'och pan caj u y ån t' ånaj C'uj: 
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj, quire' caj a ts'aja to'onex ij co'ochex pan. 
\p Caj u r åc xat'aj ti' u cams åwinicob caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïJantex a je' pana' quire' in b åq'uer. Jantex. 
\p  
\v 23 Caj ts'oc u r åc janticob yo'och pan, Jes√∫s caj u chucaj u chan ruch yejer u c'ab u wich uva. Caj u y ån t' ånaj C'uj: 
\p ‚ÄïBayo' C'uj, tech caj a ts'aja to'onex u c'ab u wich uva. 
\p Caj u ts'aja ti' u cams åwinicob, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïR åc uq'uex ca' ca' xot' techex a wu'q'uiquex u c'ab u wich uva. 
\p  
\v 24 Caj ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïA je' u c'ab u wich uva, in q'uiq'uer quir u nup'ur u t' ån a ba' tu ch'ic araj C'uj uch. A je' ba' cu bin joc'ar in q'uiq'uer soc yiric mac, ya'ab cu bin u jawsicob u si'pirob.  
\v 25 Taj quin wa'aric techex. M å' in y åny ån ca' uq'uic u c'ab u wich uva hasta cu xur t' åne', ca' bin in wuq'uej yejerex tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu tsicbar ti' Pedro: A techo' ca bin a wa'aric m å' a wer maquen 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.30‚Äë35; Lc.‚ÄØ22.31‚Äë34; Jn.‚ÄØ13.36‚Äë38) 
\p  
\v 26 Caj ts'oc u c'ayob caj joc'ob caj binob ich u witsir Olivos.  
\v 27 Jes√∫s tune', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïTechex tu cotorechex ca bin a p' åtiquenex ac'bir baje'rer quire' ca' nup'uc u t' ån C'uj tu cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúQuin cha'ic u quinsic a mac a cu c ånantic y år åc' t åm ån yuc, rajen cu bin puts'urob y år åc' t åm ån yuc.‚Äù  
\v 28 Ca' bin w åc' ås riq'uiquen tin quimirir ‚Äïquij Jes√∫s‚Äï, ti' ca bin a wiriquenex ich u ru'umin Galilea. Chen a teno' quin y ån bat'an c'uchur ich u ru'umin Galilea. 
\p  
\v 29 Pedro tune', caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïCax tu cotor in wet cams åwinicob cu bin u p' åtiquechob, chen a teno' m å' in p' åtiquech. 
\p  
\v 30 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïJach taj, quin wa'aric tech, Pedro. M å' toy c'ayn åc cax ac'bir baje'rer, cax m åna' u nup u tenin u c'ay cax, ca bin a wa'aric ti' mac: ‚ÄúM å' in wer mac Jes√∫s.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Barej raji'e' caj u jach chen a'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïCax wa quet ij quimin, m å' in wa'aric: ‚ÄúM å' in c' å'otechi'.‚Äù 
\p Bayiri' xan, caj ya'araj u yet cams åwinicob. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu t' ånic C'uj ich u chan corir Getseman√≠ 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.36‚Äë46; Lc.‚ÄØ22.39‚Äë46) 
\p  
\v 32 Caj c'uchij Jes√∫s yejer u cams åwinicob ich u chan corir u c'aba' Getseman√≠. Caj u ya'araj ti' u cams åwinicob: 
\p ‚ÄïTe' a y ån cutarexa', quire' tar quin bin bayt åc quir in t' ånic C'uj. 
\p  
\v 33 Caj u p åyaj tu pach Pedro yejer Jacobo yejer u yits'in Juan. Jes√∫s caj u y ånxchun u tucur, jach manan cu tucur caj c'uchij bayt åc.  
\v 34 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïJach tucur in caj. Cu jach bin in wor irej wa bin in caj quimin. Te' a p'atarexa' m å' a wen ånex soc a yamtiquenex. 
\p  
\v 35 Jes√∫s caj bin u t' ånej C'uj. Jach bayt åc caj bin, caj p åch'raj quir u t' ånej C'uj ich ru'um. Caj u ya'araj ti' C'uj: 
\p ‚ÄïWa tsoy ta t' ån tech Tet, wa m å' a cha'ic in jach muc'yaj an ten bic caj a toc araj uch. Wa tsoy ta t' ån tech ca cha'ic in muc'yaj, baxuc ten tsoy tin t' ån xan, ca' tac ti' ten a ba' a c'at ten. 
\p  
\v 36 Tu cu t' ånic C'uj raji' caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïIn Tetech C'uj ‚Äïquij‚Äï, c'ucha'an a wor ti' tu cotor ba', ruc'sej a je' muc'yaja' a cu bin tar ten wa ra' a c'at ca' muc'yajn åquen, je' in muc'yaje', quire' in c'at in betic a ba' a c'at teche'. 
\p  
\v 37 Caj riq'uij, caj bin ich u cams åwinicob caj yiraj cu wen ånob caj u ya'araj ti' Pedro: 
\p ‚ÄïSim√≥n, tan wa ja wen ån? M å' wa c'ucha'an a wor a muc'tic a wen ån ca' a yamtejen cax turi' hora?  
\v 38 T' ånex C'uj, soc m å' u tumtic a worex, a quisino'. Cax a chen c'at  åja'anechex soc a t' åniquex C'uj ti' ten. Chen m å' u c'uchur a worex a muc'tic a wen ånex quire' jach tac a wen ånex. 
\p  
\v 39 Caj w åc' ås bin Jes√∫s caj u w åc' ås t' ånaj u Tet, caj u ya'araj ra'iri' u caj w åc' ås t' åno'.  
\v 40 Caj ric' Jes√∫s caj w åc' ås ur ti' y ån u cams åwinicob. Caj yiraj wen ån u ca'ob, m å' u muc'tob u wen ånob. M å' u p'irir u wichob. M å' u yerob ba' u nunquicob ti' Jes√∫s.  
\v 41 Caj tar m åna' u nup u tenin ich u cams åwinicob, caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïTsoy a wen ånex baje'rer, jesej a b åjex, baje'rer, c'uchij tu q'uinin u tarob u chuquenob a teno' a baxuquenechexo', rajen tsire'ej. Bin u c'ubiquenob a mac a y ån u si'pirobe'.  
\v 42 Riq'uenex, ca' xico'onex iric a mac a c'ubiquene' ti' y ån jach bayt åc. 
\s1 Chuc Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.47‚Äë56; Lc.‚ÄØ22.47‚Äë53; Jn.‚ÄØ18.2‚Äë11) 
\p  
\v 43 Ti' toy cu tsicbar Jes√∫s barej seb caj c'uchij Judas Iscariote, raji' ti' u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s yejer once. Yet taracob jach pim mac, u r åc ch'am ånob u mascabir, bayiri' u r åc ch'am ånob che'. Tarob quire' tuchi'ta'bob ten u jach ts'urirob sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o, yejer u jach ts'urirob u cajarob u winiquirob jud√≠o, a cu ya'aric a Nuxibo', yejer u y åjcams åy åjiriob u t' ån Mois√©s.  
\v 44 M å' toy c'uchuc Judas ich Jes√∫s caj u toc araj ti'ob, a pimo': 
\p ‚ÄïA ca wiriquex in ts'uts'ic u p'uc, ra' ca chuquiquex, ca' a qui' c' åxex u c' åb, ca' a purex ti' yejer mac a cu c ånanticob ti' soc m å' u puts'ur Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 45 Seb caj u juts' u b åj ich Jes√∫s, caj ya'araj Judas ti' Jes√∫s: 
\p ‚ÄïIn w åjcams åy åjirech, in w åjcams åy åjirech. 
\p Jeroj tune', caj u ts'uts'aj u p'uc an ten bic cu naj t' ånic a cu camsic mac u winiquirob jud√≠o.  
\v 46 Robob tune', caj u m åchajob, caj u chucajob. 
\p  
\v 47 Turiri' ich a macob a ti' y ån ti' taro', caj u jitaj u mascab caj u ch' åcaj u xiquin u c'urew u jach ts'urir sacerdote, caj rac u xiquin u c'urew u jach ts'urir sacerdote.  
\v 48 Caj u t' ånaj Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin caj tarechex tera' yejer mascab, bayiri' yejer che' quir a chuquiquenex iren wa y åja'criry åjiren ba'.  
\v 49 Rajra' ti' y ånen ich carem naj tu ca naj c'ujintiquex C'uj, caj in camsechex. Biquinin m å' ta chuquenex uch? A ba' u ber ten baje'rer quire' caj u toc araj uch y åjtseq'uir u t' ån C'uj, a ts'a'b u tucuric ten C'uj quir u ts'ibtic a ba' u c'at C'uj, ra' quire' u nup'ur a ba' ts'iba'an. 
\p  
\v 50 Ra'iri' u q'uinin tu cotor u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s caj r åc puts'ob. P'at Jes√∫s tu junan. 
\s1 Puts'ij a mac a m å' uch xuruc u baquero' 
\p  
\v 51 Barej say tu pach Jes√∫s turiri' xib, m å' uch xuruc u baquer, u chen buquinm ån u winquirir yejer turiri' s åc noc', a linojo' u c'aba' u noc'. Raji' caj chucob ten a pimo'.  
\v 52 Barej caj chuquij ten a pimo' caj ts'ub u noc' caj puts'ij, ch åc' åren. 
\s1  åc åtan ch'iriquic Jes√∫s ich u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.57‚Äë68; Lc.‚ÄØ22.54‚Äë55, 63‚Äë71; Jn.‚ÄØ18.12‚Äë14, 19‚Äë24) 
\p  
\v 53 Y åjchuquirob Jes√∫s caj bin purbir Jes√∫s ich Caif√°s. Raji' u jach ts'urir tu cotor sacerdote, yejer u jer u ca' jach ts'urirob sacerdote, yejer u jach ts'urirob tu cotor u cajarob u winiquirob jud√≠o, a cu ya'aric, a Nuxibo', yejer u y åjcams åy åjirib u t' ån Mois√©s, quire' caj u much'quintob u b åj.  
\v 54 Barej Pedroje' nach bin tu pach tu cu binob Jes√∫s. C' ås nanach cu tar Pedro tac c'uchur tub re'a'an yatoch Caif√°s. Curucbar Pedro yejer a polic√≠ajo' cu q'uich, p'eri' yejerob. 
\p  
\v 55 U jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer tu cotor u ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o, tiri' u r åc much'quinm ånob u b åj quir u wayticob quir u tus taquicob u jo'r Jes√∫s soc u quinsa'rob Jes√∫s. M å' c'ucha'an yor u wayticob quir u tus taquicob u jo'r.  
\v 56 Cax jach pim mac cu tar quir u tus taquicob u jo'r Jes√∫s, m å' tu quetquintajob u t' ånob.  
\v 57 Jeroj tune', caj tarob ca'tur u winiquirob jud√≠o quir u tus taquicob u jo'r Jes√∫s, robob tan ya'aricob: 
\p  
\v 58 ‚ÄïA to'ono', tij cu'yaj ya'aric a je' xiba' cu bin u r åc jubsic carem naj tu quic naj c'ujintiquex C'uj. A je' beta'ana' yejer u c' åb mac, je' u ca' ts' åpquintic u jer carem naj ca' bin ts'ocac u man m åna' u nup u q'uinin, a m å' beta'an yejer u c' åb mac. 
\p  
\v 59 Cax baxuc cu tsicbarob m å' tu quetquintajob u t' ånobi'. 
\p  
\v 60 Jeroj tune', caj ric ch'ictar Caif√°s ich  åc åtan tu cotor u yet jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o ca' u c'atej ba' ti' Jes√∫s, tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin m å' a c' ås nunquic ti' a mac cu taquicob a jo'r tech? 
\p  
\v 61 Jes√∫s u m åcm ån u chi' uch, m å' u c' ås nunquic ti' u jach ts'urir. U jach ts'urir tu cotor sacerdote caj u w åc' ås c'atej ti' tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïArej tenob wa tech a Cristojo' a mac caj u toc araj C'uj y ån u tar quir u taquic tu cotor mac? Arej tenob wa tech u pararech C'uj a cu c'ujinta'bo' ten mac? 
\p  
\v 62 Jes√∫s caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïTen ‚Äïquij‚Äï, bin a wirenex xan a teno' a baxuquenechexo' curucbaren ich u no'oj C'uj, a jach manan chichir u muc'o'. Je' a wiriquex in tar tu muy årir ca'anan. 
\p  
\v 63 U jach ts'urir tu cotor sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o, seb caj u j åtaj u noc' quir u yesic ts'iquij, quire' cu tucra' cu pach'ic C'uj Jes√∫s an ten bic caj u nuncaj Jes√∫s, caj u ya'araj u jach ts'urir tu cotor sacerdote: 
\p ‚ÄïBa'wir ti' u jer mac quir u ta'quic u jo'r? A b åjiri'ex caj a wu'yajex cu pach'ic C'uj.  
\v 64 Arex ten ba' ca tucriquex te'ex? 
\p Robob u jach ts'urirob tu cotor u winiquirob jud√≠o, caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïToc y ån u si'pir, ca' quinsac. 
\p  
\v 65 Jun yarob caj u y ånx chun u tubob u wich, u jerob caj u pixob u wich Jes√∫s caj u raxajob xan, cu ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïArej tenob mac caj u raxech. 
\p U polic√≠a a caj u chucajobo' caj u tacj åts'ajob Jes√∫s. 
\s1 Pedro cu ya'aric: M å' in wer maqui' Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ26.69‚Äë75; Lc.‚ÄØ22.56‚Äë62; Jn.‚ÄØ18.15‚Äë18, 25‚Äë29) 
\p  
\v 66 Ti' toy y ån Pedro ich tancab tu re'a'an yatoch Caif√°s, caj u juts'aj u b åj turiri' xquic ich Pedro. Ra' u c'urew xquic Caif√°s;  
\v 67 Barej caj u yiraj cu q'uich Pedroje', caj u p åctaj, caj u ya'araj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïA tech xane' ‚Äïquij ya'ara'‚Äï, ti' a wet man Jes√∫s a cu tar tu cajar Nazaret. 
\p  
\v 68 Barej raji', caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' teni' ‚Äïquij Pedro‚Äï. M å' in wer ba' ca wa'aric. M å' in wer maqui'. 
\p Pedro caj joc' tancab bayt åc tu y ån u jor naj, jeroj caj c'ayn åj a caxo'.  
\v 69 Caj w åc' ås irir ten u c'urew xquic Caif√°s caj w åc' ås a'ara ti' a macob a ti' y ånob taro': 
\p ‚ÄïA je' xiba', jach taj, u yet man Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 70 Barej raji' caj u w åc' ås a'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' teni' ‚Äïquij caj ya'araj. 
\p Chen sansame', a mac a ti' y ånob uch taro', caj u w åc' ås a'arajob ti' Pedro: 
\p ‚ÄïJach taje' tech a wet m ån Jes√∫s uch, a m å' quet baxuc a t' ån yejer Jes√∫s quire' u xibirech u ru'umin Galilea. 
\p  
\v 71 Caj ara'b Pedro, cu chuquic C'uj, tan ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïC'uj cu yiric, wa m å' in wer a mac a ca wa'ariquexe', cax u quinsiquen C'uj. 
\p  
\v 72 Bayiri' caj ca' c'ayn åj cax tu ca' ten, Pedro caj u c'asaj yic' a ba' ara'b ten Jes√∫s uch: ‚ÄúM å' toy w åc' ås c'ayn åc a caxo' m åna' u nup u tenin ca bin a wa'aric m å' a wer maqueni'.‚Äù Pedro caj oc'n åjij. Caj jach qui' oc'n åjij Pedro tun. 
\c 15  
\s1 Jes√∫s  åc åtan ti' Pilato 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.1‚Äë2, 11‚Äë14; Lc.‚ÄØ23.1‚Äë5; Jn.‚ÄØ18.28‚Äë38) 
\p  
\v 1 Barej caj sasij seb tu cotor u jach ts'urirob sacerdote yejer u jach ts'urirob u cajarob u winiquirob jud√≠o, a cu ya'aricob a Nuxibo', yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s, yejer a mac t'irir ich tu cotor u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o, caj u much'quintajob u b åj quir u tucricob bic tabar cu bin u c'ubicob c' åxbir Jes√∫s ich Pilato. Caj c'ax u c' åb Jes√∫s caj tar purbir ich Pilato, raji' gobernador.  
\v 2 A Pilatoje' caj u c'ataj ti': 
\p ‚ÄïTaj wa ju reyech u winiquirob jud√≠o? 
\p Caj u nuncaj raji', cu ya'aric ti': 
\p ‚ÄïBaxuc ca wa'ariquen, a teno' u reyen u winiquirob jud√≠o. 
\p  
\v 3 U jach ts'urirob sacerdote, ya'ab caj u tocob u jo'r Jes√∫s.  
\v 4 A Pilatoje', caj u w åc' ås c'ataj ti', cu ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin m å' a c' ås nunquic u taquicob a jo'r quire' jach ya'ab tan u taquicob a jo'r? 
\p  
\v 5 Jes√∫s m å' u c' ås nuncaj chichin, rajen jach jaq'uij yor Pilato. 
\s1 Pilato caj u tucraj tu yor ca' xic sinbir Jes√∫s ich cruz 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.15‚Äë31; Lc.‚ÄØ23.13‚Äë25; Jn.‚ÄØ18.38‚Äï19.16) 
\p  
\v 6 Toc beri' cu siptic mac tub m åca'an ca' bin c'uchuc tu q'uinin u qui' qui' jan ånob u winiquirob jud√≠o, u q'uinin tu potmastaj y åjmasir u t' ån C'uj uch. M å' ja wirej, a gobernadoro' cu bin u siptic a mac m åca'an a cu c'ata' ti' ten u winiquirob jud√≠o.  
\v 7 A ray u q'uinino' ti' m åca'an mac jach c'as. Ra' u c'aba' Barrab√°s, raji' c' åra'an yejer u yet ric's  åjba'te'ob, mac u quinsm ånob winic tu tu ric'sajob ba'te' uch.  
\v 8 Ra' u quinin, ti' cu tarob a ya'ab macob u winiquirob jud√≠o, quir u much'quinticob u b åj ich Pilato, caj u y ånxchun u c'aticob ca' u betej an ten bic cu naj beta'r ti'obe'.  
\v 9 Pilato tune', caj u nuncaj ti'ob, cu ya'aric: 
\p ‚ÄïA mac a c'at in siptiquex techex? Arex ten ca' in siptej ti' techex u rey u winiquirob jud√≠o? 
\p  
\v 10 M å' ja wirej, Pilato yer q'uex yorob u jach ts'urirob sacerdote, rajen c'ubob Jes√∫s ten u jach ts'urirob sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o.  
\v 11 Barej u jach ts'urirob sacerdote u winiquirob jud√≠o caj u p'usaj u yorob a ya'ab macob quir u cha'b år ti'ob Barrab√°s, cax m å' u cha'b år Jes√∫s.  
\v 12 Jeroj tune', caj u nuncaj Pilato, caj u w åc' ås a'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBa' a c'atex ca' in betej ti' a mac a ca wa'ariquex u rey u winiquirob jud√≠ojo'? 
\p  
\v 13 Robob a pim macob, caj u c'amquintajob t' ånob ti' tu ca'ten: 
\p ‚ÄïArej ti' ca' xic sinbir ich cruz. 
\p  
\v 14 Barej Pilato caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïBiquinin cu bin sinbir ich cruz quire' m åna' c'as caj u betaj? 
\p Caj chen c'amquintaj u t' ånob a pimo': 
\p ‚ÄïArej ca' sinic ich cruz. 
\p  
\v 15 A Pilatoje', quire' u c'at u qui'quintic u yorob a pimo', rajen caj u cha'j u bin Barrab√°s. Caj ts'oc u j åts'icob u pach Jes√∫se', caj u c'u'saj ca' quinsac tu cruz.  
\v 16 A soldadojo' tune', caj acsa'b Jes√∫s ich palacio gobernador, tu re'a'an naj. Caj u t' ånajob u much'quinticob u b åj tu cotor u yet soldadojob gobernador.  
\v 17 Caj pit u noc' Jes√∫s ten soldadojo', caj ts'a'b u buquintej ch åc noc' Jes√∫s. Caj jit'ob a q'ui'ixer u ca'o' quir u ts'a'b år u p'oquintej Jes√∫s q'ui'ix.  
\v 18 Jeroj tune', caj chinrajob  åc åtan ti' Jes√∫s ten a soldadojo', caj u tus t' ånajob an ten bic cu naj t' ånicob rey cu ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïIn c'atob ca' cuxraquech munt q'uin u reyech u winiquirob jud√≠o. 
\p  
\v 19 Caj u c'oc'oj åts'tajob tu jo'r Jes√∫s yejer j år år, caj u tubob u wich. Ti' r åc xonr åjob ich  åc åtan Jes√∫s an ten bic cu xontarob ich rey cu tus esicob u s åjticob ti'.  
\v 20 Barej caj ts'oc u p'asticobe', caj u pitajob a ch åc noq'ue', a tu tus ts'ajob sam ti'e' caj u buquintajob u w åc' ås noc' caj u joc'sajob quir u quinsa'r tu cruz. 
\s1 Sinbir Jes√∫s tu cruz 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.32‚Äë44; Lc.‚ÄØ23.26‚Äë43; Jn.‚ÄØ19.17‚Äë27) 
\p  
\v 21 A uche' caj u man taro' turiri' xib, u c'aba' Sim√≥n, u tet Alejandro yejer Rufo. A Sim√≥no' caj tar tu ru'umin Cirene uch. Cu yu'ur tu cor caj ts'ar u pach quir u c'o'ochic u cruz Jes√∫s tu cu bin b åjbir.  
\v 22 Caj u p åyajob Jes√∫s tu chan witsir u c'aba' G√≥lgota, u c'at ya'aric: U Cuchir U Baquer U Jo'r.  
\v 23 Caj u tumtaj ca' ts'ab åc u c'ab u wich uva u yuq'uej, aro' xaca'an u ts'ac mirra, barej raji'e' m å' tu yuc'aji'.  
\v 24 Jeroj tune', caj ts'oc u baj år Jes√∫s ten soldadojob caj u j åsajob u noc' Jes√∫s caj u chictajob chan tunich quir yiric mac cu bin u ch'ic u noc' Jes√∫s. Soc yerob ba' cu bin ch'ic jujunturob. 
\p  
\v 25 Ca'anan u q'uinin, jach jats'cab caj u sinajob tu cruz.  
\v 26 Ts'ibta'b ich c' ås chumuc u jo'r u cruz Jes√∫s, irej wa ju cuchir ts'ib quir yiric ba' u si'pir. Caj u ts'ibtaj: ‚ÄúA je' xiba' Jes√∫s, u rey u winiquirob jud√≠o.‚Äù  
\v 27 Caj u sinajob tu cruz yejer raji' ca'tur xib, a cu ya'cricob ba'. Caj baj ten soldado. Turiri' tu noj Jes√∫s, turiri' tu ts'ic xan Jes√∫s.  
\v 28 Rajen toc nup'a'an a ba' ts'iba'an ich u t' ån C'uj a cu ya'aric: ‚ÄúCaj u tucrajob wa raji' p'eri' yejer a mac a y ån u si'pirobe'.‚Äù  
\v 29 A macob a cu manob uche' taro', caj u p'astajob, caj u chictob u jo'r an bic cu naj p'asticob mac, tan ya'aricob: 
\p ‚ÄïA techo' ca wa'aric je' a jubsic carem naj, ca wa'aric m åna' u nup u q'uinin a w åc' ås ts' åpquintej u jer carem naj.  
\v 30 Tac a b åj ich a cruz, w åc' ås emen ta cruz. 
\p  
\v 31 Ti' y ånob xan, caj u p'astob Jes√∫s u jach ts'urirob, cu pacran ya'aricob, quet yejer y åjcams åy åjirob u t' ån Mois√©s: 
\p ‚ÄïA ray xibo', chen u jer cu taquic, u b åjiri' m å' c'ucha'an u muc' u w åc' ås taquic u b åji'.  
\v 32 Ca' ij quirex wa raji' Cristo, a mac tuchi'ta'b ten C'uj, u rey u winiquirob Israel. Ca' emac tu cruz baje'rer, ca' in wirejob soc ca' in wacsejob tin worob ti'. Baxuc xan, u yet b åja'an winiquirob caj u p'astajob ti'. 
\s1 Quimij Jes√∫s 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.45‚Äë56; Lc.‚ÄØ23.44‚Äë49; Jn.‚ÄØ19.28‚Äë30) 
\p  
\v 33 Caj c'uchij c'ac'chun q'uin caj ac'birch åjij ich yoc'ocab tac u man m åna' u nup horas.  
\v 34 Tabar u c'uchur a m åna' u nup horaso' caj c'am t' ån åj Jes√∫s caj aw åtn åjij, caj ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïEloi, Eloi, lama sabactani? ‚Äïu c'at ya'aric: In C'ujech, in C'ujech, biquinin ca p' åtiquen tin junan? 
\p  
\v 35 Barej caj u'yab ten jun yarob a mac a ti' y ånob ti' taro', caj u ya'arob: 
\p ‚ÄïU'yex ba' cu ya'aric. Cu t' ånic El√≠as, y åjtsequir u t' ån C'uj. 
\p  
\v 36 Caj u c' ånaj yacab turiri' tu y ån ya'arir a p åj u c'ab u wich uva, caj u ts' åmaj u noq'uir quir u ts'uts'ic ya'arir a p åj u c'ab u wich uvajo'. Caj u chucaj caj u t åcaj tu che'er j år år quir u nacsic u ts'a ti' yuq'uej. Caj u ts'aj u yuq'uej caj ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïPajo'onex, ca' ij quirex wa cu bin tar El√≠as, ca' u yensej tu cruz Jes√∫s. 
\p  
\v 37 Barej Jes√∫s caj c'am t' ånaj, caj u putaj yic', caj quimij.  
\v 38 U noc' a t'ina'ano' ich carem naj tu cu naj c'ujinticob C'uj u winiquirob jud√≠o, a cu j åsic jun xot' naj tu cu bin u wa'quic u q'uiq'uer y år åc' soc u ruc'sic u si'pirob mac. Ra' u noq'uir seb caj jat chumuc. Caj u y ånxchun u jat år ca'anan tac u c'uchur u jat år ich u xax u noq'uir.  
\v 39 U jach ts'urir cien soldadojob u winiquirob romano, a ti' y ån uch  åc åtan ich Jes√∫s, caj u yiraj ts'oc u quimin an ten bic a jera', caj u ya'araj: 
\p ‚ÄïA je' xiba' jach taj u parar C'uj. 
\p  
\v 40 Baxuc xan, ti' y ånob jun yarob xquicob, c' ås nach cu p åcticob Jes√∫s a ray xquicob. Ti' y ånob Mar√≠a, ra' c åja'an tu cajar Magadalena, ti' y ån Mar√≠a u n å' Jacobo a chichano', yejer Jos√©, ti' y ån xan Salom√©.  
\v 41 Ra' yet manacob yejer Jes√∫s caj tarob tu pach Jes√∫s. Caj tarob tu pach Jes√∫s caj u p' åtaj u ru'umin Galilea. Quire' ti' y ån ich u ru'umin Galilea. Robob caj u yamtajob Jes√∫s, ti' y ån u jer ya'ab xquicob caj binob uch tu cajar Jerusal√©n yejer Jes√∫s. 
\s1 Caj t'oj u baquer Jes√∫s ich japnin tunich 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ27.57‚Äë61; Lc.‚ÄØ23.50‚Äë56; Jn.‚ÄØ19.38‚Äë42) 
\p  
\v 42 Barej caj ac'birch åjij, raji' u q'uinin cu pac much'quinticob yo'och quir u qui' qui' jan ånob. M å' ja wirej, saman u q'uinin u jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o.  
\v 43 Caj tarij Jos√©, ti' cu tar ich u cajar Arimatea, raji' turiri' ich tu cotor u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o, a mac tsoy yor, ich u jach ts'urirob u winiquirob jud√≠o. Raji' xan, cu pajic u q'uinin tu cu bin u reyinticob C'uj. Caj u chichquintaj u yor quir u bin ich  åc åtan Pilato quir u c'atic u baquer Jes√∫s quir u but'ic tu japnin tunich Jos√©.  
\v 44 Jac' yor Pilato, quire' toc quimij Jes√∫s, caj u tuchi'taj t' ånbir u jach ts'urir cien soldadojob u winiquirob romano, caj u c'ataj ti' wa taj toc quimij Jes√∫s.  
\v 45 Barej caj u yubaj tu chi' tu jach ts'urir cien soldadojob u winiquirob romano, caj yubaj ya'aric wa quimij Jes√∫s tu ts'aj u baquer ti' Jos√©.  
\v 46 Raji'e' caj u m ånaj turiri' s åc noc', lino u c'aba' a s åc noq'ue', caj ts'oc u yensic u baquer caj u tapaj yejer a s åc noq'ue', caj bin u but'ej ich japnin tunich, ra' toc beta'b u japnin uch ti' tunich. Jeroj tune', caj u b åc' åstaj turiri' tunich tu jor u japnin tunich quir u qui' pe'che'tic.  
\v 47 Mar√≠a a cu tar tu cajar Magdalena yejer Mar√≠a u n å' Jos√© uche', caj u p åctob tu bin t'ajbir u baquer Jes√∫s. 
\c 16  
\s1 Riq'uij Jes√∫s tu quimirir 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ28.1‚Äë10; Lc.‚ÄØ24.1‚Äë12; Jn.‚ÄØ20.1‚Äë10) 
\p  
\v 1 Barej caj man u q'uinin tu cu jesicob u b åj u winiquirob jud√≠o, Mar√≠a, a cu tar tu cajar Magdalena, quet yejer Mar√≠a, u n å' Jacobo, quet yejer xan Salom√©, robob caj u m ånajob a qui' u boc soc c'ucha'an yorob u chojicob u baquer Jes√∫s.  
\v 2 U q'uinin u y ånxchun semana, jach a'ac'bir tan u tar q'uin caj tarob tu t'aja'an u baquer Jes√∫s.  
\v 3 Cu pacran a'aricob a xquico': 
\p ‚ÄïMac cu bin u b åc' åstic ti' to'onex a tunicho' a ti' y ån tu jor a tu t'aja'an u baquero'? 
\p  
\v 4 Caj c'uchob caj u nacsaj u wichobe', caj u yirajob a jach carem tuniche', toc b åc' åsa'an.  
\v 5 Barej caj ocob tu t'aja'an u baquer Jes√∫s, caj u yirajob turiri' xib, m å' uch xuruc u baqueri'. Ti' c'ura'an tu noj a xquique'. Raji' u buquinm ån jach c' år åp s åc noc'. Caj jaq'uij yorob a xquico', caj yirob curic.  
\v 6 Barej raji'e', caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' u jac' år a worex ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ca c åxtiquex Jes√∫s, a cu tar tu cajar Nazaret uche', a mac quinsa'b tu cruz. W åc' ås riq'uij, m åna' Jes√∫s tera' ‚Äïquij‚Äï, ca' cuxrajij ‚Äïquij‚Äï te' y ån u wa'aya' tu chaquinta'b u baquer ucha', iric ‚Äïquij‚Äï.  
\v 7 Barej xenex, arex ti' u cams åwinicob, quet a wa'ariquex ti', yejer Pedro: ‚ÄúArex ti'ob cu bin tu ru'umin Galilea, raji' cu bin y ån bat'an c'uchur. A techexo', pachir a c'uchurex. Ti' ca bin a wirex aro' an ten bic caj u toc araj techex uch.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Caj joc'ob ich tu t'aja'an u baquer Jes√∫s uch, caj u c' ånajob yacab quir u puts'urob quire' jach manan saj åcob, tu chen quiquir ånc årob. M åna' ba' caj u ya'arajob ti', quire' jach saj åcob. 
\s1 Irir Jes√∫s ten Mar√≠a a cu tar tu cajar Magdalena 
\r (Jn.‚ÄØ20.11‚Äë18) 
\p  
\v 9 Barej caj riq'uij Jes√∫s ti' u quimirir, a'ac'bir, u q'uinin u y ånxchun semana, caj u y ån bat'an esaj u b åj ti' Mar√≠a, a cu tar tu cajar Magdalena, ra'iri' Mar√≠a a joc'sa'b siete u quisinob ten Jes√∫s uch.  
\v 10 Caj bin Mar√≠a, caj u ya'araj ti' u yet manob uch Jes√∫s, caj c'uchij Mar√≠a cu yoc'arob, cu yacticob Jes√∫s.  
\v 11 Robobe', cax caj u yubajob cuxa'ane', cax yubobo' irir ten Mar√≠a. Robob caj u ya'arajob: 
\p ‚ÄïM å' taji' ‚Äïquij. 
\s1 Irir Jes√∫s ten ca'tur u cams åwinicob Jes√∫s 
\r (Lc.‚ÄØ24.13‚Äë35) 
\p  
\v 12 Barej pachir ca'tur caj u yirajob m å' irej Cristo, caj u yirajob quire' jarp åjij quimij, cu binob ximbar ich ch åc ån, caj u yirajobi'.  
\v 13 Caj binob, robobe' ya'arej ti' u rac'ob, barej, m å' ju quibob caj yubob ya'ara' ti'ob, xan. 
\s1 Jes√∫s cu ts'ic u beyaj ti' u cams åwinicob 
\r (Mt.‚ÄØ28.16‚Äë20; Lc.‚ÄØ24.36‚Äë49; Jn.‚ÄØ20.19‚Äë23) 
\p  
\v 14 Pachir caj u yesaj u b åj cuxa'an ti' a oncejo' u cams åwinicob tu junanob, quire' curucbarob tu jan ånob. Caj q'ueya'bob ti'ob quire' cax ara'b ti'ob ten y åjirirob Jes√∫s, chen m å' ju yacsob tu yorob wa riq'uij. Caj q'ueya'bob xan, quire' chich u jo'rob.  
\v 15 Caj u ya'araj ti'ob: 
\p ‚ÄïJoq'uenex ca' a tsec'tex u jach tsoyir u t' ån C'uj ich tu cotor mac ich yoc'ocab.  
\v 16 A mac a cu yacsic tu yor bayiri' xan, tan yacsa' ja' tu jo'r, bin tocac ten C'uj. Barej a mac a m å' ju yacsej tu yor, ti' toy y ån u si'pir quire' m å' ju yacsaj tu yore', raji' cu bin sat åre'.  
\v 17 A ba' m åna' mac yirm åni' uch, m å' biq'uin yirm åni', ra' cu bin esbir ten an mac a yacsm ånob tu yorob an ten bic a jera': Bin u joc'sicob quisinob quire' ten tin ts'aja u muc'ob. Bin u tsicbarob ich u t' ån a mac m å' u najticob uchi'.  
\v 18 Wa cu chuquic can, cax wa cu yuq'uic a ba' cu quinsic mac, m å' u bin c'astar. Bin u cu ts'anc' åbtic a mac yaje', jeroj cu jaw åra'. 
\s1 Jes√∫s caj bin ca'anan 
\r (Lc.‚ÄØ24.50‚Äë53) 
\p  
\v 19 A Jaj Ts'uro', caj ts'oc u tsicbar yejerob caj bin ca'anano', caj curaj ich u no'oj C'uj quir u s åjta' ten tu cotor mac.  
\v 20 U cams åwinicob Jes√∫s tune', caj joc'obe' quir u tsec'ticob u t' ån Jes√∫s ti' tu cotor mac, jach quet u beyaj u Jaj Ts'urir yejerob. A Jaj Ts'uro' caj u yesaj a ba' cu tsicbarob u cams åwinicob ra' taj cu ya'aricob. Jeroj Ts'oquij, quij.